\id REV - Tuivang Holy Bible 
\h AWIPHAWNG 
\toc1 Awiphawng 
\toc2 Awiphawng 
\toc3 Awph 
\mt1 AWIPHAWNG  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Jesu Khrih ak awiphawng, ak law hly kawi ik-oeih, a tyihzawihkhqi venawh dang sak aham Khawsa ing a venawh a peek taw vemyihna awm hy. A tyihzawih Johan a venawh ak khan ceityih tyi nawh dangsak hy,  
\v 2 anih ing a huh ik-oeihkhqi boeih ce kqawn hy – cawhkaw ik-oeih cetaw, Khawsa ak awi ingkaw Jesu Khrih a sim saknaak awi ceni.  
\v 3 Vawhkaw kqawn oepchoeh na ak awm awi ak noet taw a zoseen hy, ve ak awi ak zakhqi boeih ingkaw ce a ik-oeih qee na ak awmkhqi boeih ce ak kawk khuiawh ak khoem taw a zoseen hy, kawtih atym taw zoe hawh hy.   
\p
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Ex. 3.14; \xt Awph 4.5.\x*Johan ing, Asia ram awhkaw thlangboel khqih a venawh: Ak awm hui, ak awm hawh ingkaw ak awm law hly ingkaw amah a ngawihdoelh a hai awhkaw myihla Khrih ingkaw,  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Is. 55.4; \xt Sam 89.27.\x*ypawm simpyikung, thlakthi anglakawhkaw ak thang cyk, khawmdek sangpahrangkhqi boeih ak ukkung Jesu Khrih a venawh kaw qeennaak ingkaw ngaihdingnaak nangmih a venawh awm seh. Ningmih ni lung nak khqi nawh amah a thi ing thawlhnaak ak khuiawh kawng ningnih anik loet sak khqikung,  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Ex. 19.6; Awph 5.10.\x*a Khawsa ingkaw Pa a bibi aham ningnih ce a ram awhkaw pilnam ingkaw Khawsoihkhqi na anik saikung a venawh thang leeknaak ingkaw thaawmnaak kumqui dy awm seh! Amen.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Dan. 7.13; Mat 24.30; Marka 13.26; Luke 21.27; 1Th 4.17; \xt Zech. 12.10; Joh 19.34,37; \xt Zech. 12.10; Mat 24.30.\x*Toek lah, myi awh law kawmsaw, mik a hoei ing amah ce hu kaw, amah cai ing ak sunkungkhqi ingawm; khawmdek thlangkhqi boeih ing anih awh ce khy am kqang kawm uh. Ce myihna awm seh! Amen  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Awph 22.13; \xt Ex. 3.14.\x*Kai taw Alpha ingkaw Omega na awm nyng,” tinawh “ak awm hui, ak awm hawh ingkaw ak law hly kawi, Bawimang,” Bawipa ing kqawn hy.   
\p
\v 9 Kai, Johan, nangmih a koeinaa na ak awm nawh Jesu awh ningnih aham ak awm qam ingkaw khuikhanaak ak yh haih, taw Khawsak awi ingkaw Jesu akawng kak kqawn dawngawh Patmos sanglak cung awh awm nyng.  
\v 10 10 Bawipa nyn awh Myihla ing awm nyng saw, ka huben na kawng uut awi amyihna awi khawteh ce za nyng,  
\v 11 ce ak awi ing: \wj “Na huh ve cazawl awh qee nawhtaw thlangboel khqih tloek: Ephesa, Smyrna, Pergamum, Thyatira, Sardis, Philadelphia ingkaw Laodicea a venawh pat pe,”\wj* ni tina hy.  
\v 12 Ka venawh awi ak kqawn lawkung ce toek aham hawi qunyng. Kang hawi qu awh sui mai vangnaak khqih ce hu nyng,  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Dan. 7.13; \xt Dan. 10.5.\x*cawhkaw mai vangnaak ak khuiawh pynoet taw, “thlanghqing capa myihna awm hy,” khawkkhik dy ak pha suibai ing thawicam qu nawh ak kqang awh sui hi ca ing zeen qu hy.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Dan. 7.9.\x*\x - \xo 1:14 \xt Dan. 10.6.\x*A lu ingkaw a lusam taw tuu a myi myihna bawk nawh vyl a myihna bawk hy, a mik qawi taw maikqawng a myihna awm hy.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Ezek. 1.24; 43.2.\x*A khaw qawi taw mai awh qawhum hloei a myihna vang hy, ak awi taw tui ang lawng tha ak awm soeih a myihna awm hy.  
\v 16 Ak tang kut awh aihchi khqih pawm nawh am kha awh hu hai ak hrat zawzi ce thoeng hy. A hai taw khawmik a ling hui awhkaw myihna awm hy.   
\p
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Is. 44.6; 48.12; Awph 2.8; 22.13.\x*Anih ce ka huh awh, thlakthi myihna a khaw kung awh tlu hqoeng nyng. Cawh kak khanawh ak tang kut ce tloeng law nawh: \wj “Koeh kqih. Kai taw ak kqannaak ingkaw a dytnaak na awm nyng. \wj* 
\v 18 \wj Kai taw ak hqing thlang na awm nyng; thi hlai nyng, ngai lah kumqui ingkaw kumqui dy na hqing nyng! Thihnaak ingkaw Hades cabi ce ta nyng. \wj* 
\v 19 \wj Cedawngawh, tuh ak awm ingkaw ak awm hly ik-oeih na huh ce qeel ah. \wj* 
\v 20 \wj Kak tang benawh aihchi khqih ang hyp ik-oeih ingkaw sui mai vangnaak khqih na huh cetaw veni: Aihchi khqih cetaw thlangboel khqih tloek ak khan ceityihkhqi na awm nawh mai vangnaak khqih tloek cetaw thlangboel khqih tloek ce \wj*ni.   
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 \wj Ephesa khaw awhkaw thlangboel khan ceityih a venawh qee lah: Ve ak awi taw ak tang benawh aihchi khqih ak pawm ingkaw sui maivangnaak khqih anglakawh ak cet thlang ak awi na awm hy. \wj* 
\v 2 \wj Na ik-oeih sainaak, tha tlawh doena bi na binaak ingkaw, yh thainaak na taaknaakkhqi ce sim nyng. Thlakchekhqi am toek poek thai hyk ti, ceityih na ak sa qukhqi noek a dak tiksaw a hqawng ni amik kqawn hy tice hu hyk ti. \wj* 
\v 3 \wj Kai ang ming awh kyinaak yh ngah ngah tiksaw nak tha am se hy. \wj* 
\v 4 \wj Cehlai na lungnaak lamma ce na hoet a dawngawh vawh ka ni oelhnaak awm hy. \wj* 
\v 5 \wj Ak sang nakawng nang tlaaknaak ce poek lah! Zut nawhtaw lamma awhkaw na saikhqi ce sai tlaih lah. Am nang zut awhtaw, na venawh law kawng nyng saw na maivang ce a awmnaak hun awhkawng thoeih law valh kawng nyng. \wj* 
\v 6 \wj Cehlai ve a ik-oeih sai ngaihnaak ce ta hyk ti: Nikolaitan a ik-oeih saikhqi ce sawh na hyk ti, kai ingawm sawh na lawt nyng. \wj* 
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Gen 2.9; Awph 22.2; \xt Ezek. 28.13; 31.8.\x*\wj Haa ak ta ingtaw, Myihla ing thlangboelkhqi venawh ak kqawn ce za seh. Noengnaak ak takhqi venawh, Khawsa a paradise ak khuiawh ak awm hqingnaak thikthaih ai thainaak ce pe kawng.\wj*   
\p
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Is. 44.6; 48.12; Awph 1.17; 22.13.\x*\wj Smyrna khaw awhkaw thlangboel khan ceityih a venawh qee lah: Ve ak awi taw lamma ingkaw hudyt na ak awm, thi hlai hy ak hqing tlaih ak awikhqi ni. \wj* 
\v 9 \wj Khuikha nawh hahqah hyk ti tice sim nyng – cehlai boei hyk ti! Judah thlangkhqi amyihna thlang ak kqawn seetkhqi ce Juda thlangkhqi amni, sinakawk awhkaw setankhqi ni. \wj* 
\v 10 \wj Khuikhanaak hly kawi awh ce koeh kqih ka nik kqawn law peek khqi ve, setan ing nangmih ak khui awhkaw thlang vang ce noek a dak aham thawng khuina nik thlak khqi kaw, hqa nyn khuiawh khuikha naak hu kawm uk ti. Thih dyna ypawm na awm lah, hqingnaak boei lumyk ce ni pe kawng. \wj* 
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Awph 20.14; 21.8.\x*\wj U awm haa ak ta ingtaw, thlangboelkhqi venawh Myihla ing ak kqawn peek awi ce za seh. Noengnaak ak ta thlang taw a hih voei thihnaak ing am tlawh sak qoe voel kaw.\wj*   
\p
\v 12 Pergamum khaw awhkaw thlangboel khan ceityih a venawh qee lah: Ve ak awi taw hu hai na ak hqat zawzi ak takung ak awikhqi ni.  
\v 13 Setan ing ngawihdoelh a taaknaak – na awmnaak ce sim nyng. Cehlai kang ming awh a tak na awm poe hyk ti. Kai awh cangnaak ce am hlat taak hyk ti, kai a ypawm simpyikung na ak awm Antipas a awm awh awm, anih ce Setan a awmnaak na khawk bau khuiawh him uhy.  
\v 14 Cehlai, ka ni oelhnaak ik-oeih a khoehca awm hy: Balak ce Isarelkhqi a zoek sak coengawh myiqawl bawknaak buh a an ai sak nawh thawlh sak ham ingkaw nu ingkaw pa thawlhnaak sai aham ak cawngpyi Balam a cawngpyinaak ak ngai thlangkhqi nangmih a venawh awm hy.  
\v 15 Cemyih nani kolaitan a cawngpyinaak ak hquutkhqi awm nangmih ak khuiawh awm bai hy.  
\v 16 Cedawngawh zut lah! Cemyih am mantaw, na venawh law zy kawng nyng saw kam kha awhkaw zawzi ing cekkhqi ce tuk kawng.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Ex. 16.14,15; 16.33,34; Joh 6.48-50; \xt Is. 62.2; 65.15.\x*U awm haa ak ta ingtaw, thlangboelkhqi venawh Myihla ing ak kqawn peek awi ce za seh. Ak noeng thlangkhqi venawh, ang hyp mana ce pe kawng. Ak hukhqi doeng ing ni a sim, ming thai qeenaak lungbawk ce pe kawng nyng.   
\p
\v 18 Thyatira khaw awhkaw thlangboel khan ceityih a venawh qee lah: Vetaw a mik mai amyihna kqawng nawh a khaw qawhum hloei amyihna ak vang, Khawsa a Capak awikhqi ni.  
\v 19 Na ik-oeih sainaak, nak cangnaak ingkaw lungnaak, na bibinaak ingkaw yhnaak, lamma awhkaw na sai anglakawh tuh khawzah khqoet sai hyk ti tice sim nyng.  
\v 20 Cehlai ve a dawngawh ka ni oelhnaak awm hy: amah ingkaw amah tawngha ak ti nu Jezebel te toek hyk ti. A cawngpyinaak ak caming ka tyihzawihkhqi nu pa thawlh sainaak ingkaw myiqawl bawknaak lucik buh a ankhqi ainaak benna sawi kang hawh hy.  
\v 21 Khawboe seet a sainaak a dawngawh zutnaak aham a tym ka peek hlai am ngaih hy.  
\v 22 Cedawngawh kyinaak ihkhun awh buuk kawng nyng saw, ak samphaih thlangkhqi awm anih a cehnaak lam awhkawng a mami zut awhtaw ce a nu ingqawi kyinaak huh sak kawng.  
\v 23 Kai ing ce a nu a cakhqi ce him pe kawng nyng. Cawh thlangboel boeih ing kai ce thlang a lingbyi kawlung ak suikung ni ti sim kawm uh, kai ing nami ik-oeih sainaak amyihna ni sam khqi boeih kawng.  
\v 24 Thyatira khaw awh ak awm thlak chang, ce a nu a cawngpyinaak amak tukhqi ingkaw Setan a awihdung amak cawngkhqi “Kai ing phyihqih amni phyih sak khqi kawng:”  
\v 25 Na taak cemah ka law hlan dy tu khak lah.  
\v 26 Noengnaak ak taakhqi ingkaw a boet dyna ak kawngaih ak saikhqi taw, qamkhqik khanawh sai thainaak ce pe kawng –  
\v 27 Anih ing cekkhqi ce thi sawnghqawl ing uk khqi kawmsaw, cekkhqi ce am amyihna khawng khqi kqek kqek kaw – kai ing ka pa a venna kaw saithainaak ka huh lawt amyihna.  
\v 28 Kai ingawm anih ce mymcang thaike ce pe kawng nyng.  
\v 29 U awm haa ak ta ingtaw, Myihla ing thlangboelkhqi venawh ak kqawn awi ce za seh.   
\c 3  
\p
\v 1 \wj Sardis khaw awhkaw khan ceityih a venawh qee lah: Vawhkaw awikhqi vetaw Khawsa Myihla khqih ingkaw aihchi khqih ak bawmkung ak awikhqi ni. Na ik-oeih sainaak ce sim nyng, ak hqing a myihna tyk hlai hyk ti thi hyk ti. \wj* 
\v 2 \wj Tho lah! ak thi tawm na pum ce tha awm sak lah, ka Khawsa a mik huh awh na ik-oeih sainaak ak soep te am hu nyng. \wj* 
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Mat 24.43,44; Luke 12.39,40; Awph 16.15.\x*\wj Cedawngawh, ik-oeih na huh ingkaw nang zaak ce poek lah, ce ak awi ce ngai nawhtaw zut lah. Cehlai amna thawh awhtaw, quk-ai a myihna law kawng nyng, ityk awh na venawh ka law tice am sim kawp ti. \wj* 
\v 4 \wj Cehlai bainaak amak kawlh thlang a khoeh Sardis khaw awh awm hyn hy. Ce mihkhqi cetaw hik bawk bai kawm usaw kai ing cet haih kawng unyng, cekkhqi cetaw kai mi ceh aham ak tyng khqi ni. \wj* 
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Ex. 32.32,33; Sam 69.28; Awph 20.12; \xt Mat 10.32; Luke 12.8.\x*\wj Cekkhqi myihna ak noeng thlangkhqi taw hik bawk bai lawt kawm uh. Anih ang ming ce ityk awh awm hqingnaak cabu khui awhkawng am hqe pe kawng, ka Pa ingqawi khan ceityih haiawh ang ming ce kai ing simpyi lawt kawng. \wj* 
\v 6 \wj U awm haa ak ta ingtaw, Myihla ing thlangboelkhqi venawh ak kqawn peek awi ce za seh.\wj*   
\p
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Is. 22.22; Job 12.14.\x*\wj Philadelphia khaw awhkaw thlangboel khan ceityih a venawh qee lah: Ve ak awikhqi vetaw a kut awh David a cabi ak awm, thlakciim ingkaw ak thym ak awi ni. Anih ing am awng ce u ingawm am khai thai kawmsaw, a khaih ce u ingawm am awng thai kaw. \wj* 
\v 8 \wj Na ik-oeih sainaak ce sim nyng. Toek lah, U ingawm ama khaih thai chawh ak awng qu ce na haiawh ta law nyng. Nak tha am awm hlai hy, kak awi ce khoem tiksaw kang ming ce am oelh hyk ti. \wj* 
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Is. 49.23; 60.14; \xt Is. 43.4.\x*\wj Setan a sinakawk na ak awmkhqi, Juda thlang na am awm loei saw ak sa qu thlangkhqi qaai ak kqawnkhqi ce – nangmih a venawh law sak kawng nyngsaw nangmih a khawkung awh khuk sym sak kawng, nangmih kai ing ni lungna nyng tice cekkhqi ing sim kawm uh. \wj* 
\v 10 \wj Kak awipeek ce kawdungnaak ing nami yh a dawngawh kai ingawm khawmdek pum khanawh ak awm thlangkhqi noekdak aham ak law hly kawi kyinaak khuiawh kawng ni hoep khqi kawng. \wj* 
\v 11 \wj Law nai hawh kawng. U ingawm boei lumyk ce ama ni qawtnaak aham na taak ce ak cakna tu khak lah. \wj* 
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Awph 21.2; \xt Is. 62.2; 65.15.\x*\wj Ak noeng thlang cetaw ka Khawsa a tempul ak tung na sai kawng nyng. Cawhkawng ityk awh awm am cehta voel kaw. Anih a dawngawh ka Khawsang ming ing ka Khawsa a khawk bau ming ce qee pe kawng nyngsaw; kang ming thai ce awm qee pe kawng. \wj* 
\v 13 \wj U awm haa ak ta ingtaw, thlangboelkhqi venawh Myihla ing ak kqawn peek awi ce za seh.\wj*   
\p
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Awicyih 8.22.\x*\wj Laodicea khaw awhkaw thlangboel khan ceityih a venawh awh qee lah: Ve ak awikhqi taw Amen, ypawm ingkaw dyihthing thym, Khawsa ik-oeih sai ak ukkung ak awikhqi ni. \wj* 
\v 15 \wj Na bibinaak ce sim nyng, ding awm am ding tiksaw ling awm am ling hyk ti. Pynoet na na awm qep aham ngaih hlai nyng! \wj* 
\v 16 \wj Na oih kqoeng a dawngawh – ling awm am ling hyk ti, ding awm am ding hyk ti – kam khak khuiawh kawng ni sa tawm hawh nyng. \wj* 
\v 17 \wj Namah ingtaw, ‘boei nyng, khawhthem awm ta nyng ikaw awm am ngoe voel nyng,’ tihyk ti. Ngaihak khawbing, qeen ak kap, khawdeng, mikhyp ingkaw ak pum a zal na na awm ce am sim hyk ti. \wj* 
\v 18 \wj Na boeinaak aham kai a venawh kaw sui mai awh a hloei ce ve thlai lah; chahnaak ak awm ak pum a zal na na awmnaak ce na singdahnaak aham hik bawk ve thlai lah; khaw na huhnaak thai aham miksi ve sak lah. \wj* 
\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Awicyih 3.12; Heb 12.6.\x*\wj Ka lungnaak thlang ce toel nyngsaw cuk am kik nyng. Cedawngawh ak thym na awm nawh zut lah. \wj* 
\v 20 \wj Ngai lah chawmkeng awh dyi nyng saw khoek nyng. U ingawm kak awi ce za nawh chawh ce am awng awhtaw, kun kawng nyng saw anih ing buh ai haih kawng nyng, anih awm kai a venawh awm lawt kaw. \wj* 
\v 21 \wj Kai ing ka noeng a dawngawh ka Pa a ngawihdoelh awh ka ning ngawih haih amyihna, ak noeng thlang cetaw boei ngawihdoelh awh kai ing ngawih haih thainaak ce pe kawng. \wj* 
\v 22 \wj U awm haa ak ta ingtaw, Myihla ing thlangboelkhqi venawh ak kqawn peek awi ce za seh. \wj*   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 Cekcoengawh ka toek hlai, ka haiawh khan chawh ak awng qu ce hu nyng. Ka venawh uut awi amyihna lamma cyk na kang zaak awi ing, “Hang law lah, vek coengawh ak awm hly kawi ce nim huh vang,” ni tina hy.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Ezek. 1.26-28; 10.1.\x*Cawh Myihla ing awm pahoei nih nyng, ka haiawh khan boei ngawihdoelh awh thlang pynoet ce hu nyng.  
\v 3 Ce boei ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi thlang ce jasper ingkaw karnelian ing lo qu hy nih. Lungsen suisak amyihna thlimha ing zawl khoep hy.  
\v 4 Cawhkaw boei ngawihdoelh ce ak chang boei ngawihdoelh a thong pupthli ce ngawi hy. Cawhkaw a hqamcakhqi cetaw hik bawk bai unawh ami lu awh sui lumyk myk boeih uhy.  
\v 5 Boei ngawihdoelh a venawh kawng khawkphla amyihna vang hlap hlap nawh khawhum ak awi amyihna ce hum hy. Boei ngawihdoelh a haiawh, maivang khqih ce vang uhy. Cawhkaw maivang cetaw Khawsa Myihla khqih ni.  
\v 6 Boei ngawihdoelh a hai cetaw hlalang ak cil soeih tuicun amyihna awm hy. Boei ngawihdoelh ing ak chung khoep ang lung kir awh, a hai ben ingkaw a hu benawh mik hqoeng na ak awm k-oeih sai ak hqing pupthli awm hy.  
\v 7 Lamma cyk awhkaw ik-oeih sai ak hqing pynoet taw samthyyn ing lo qu hy nih, apak thumnaak taw thlanghqing amyihna haai tahy, a pupthlinaak taw huu ak ding huili amyihna awm hy.  
\v 8 Cawhkaw ik-oeih sai ak hqing pupthli tloek ing ang hla kquk ta boeih nawh a pum boeih ce mik hqoeng na awm hy, ang hla ak kep awh awm mik ce awm hy. Than dai a boet kaa qoena: “Ak ciim, ak ciim, ak ciim taw Boeimang Bawipa Khawsa ni, anih taw ak awm hawh, ak awm huili ingkaw ak awm hly kawi na awm hy,” tinawh khy uhy.  
\v 9 Cawhkaw ik-oeih sai ak hqingkhqi ing thangleeknaak, kqihchahnaak ingkaw ymnaak ce boei ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi kumqui ak hqing a venawh ami peek awh,  
\v 10 boei ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi a hqamca a thong pupthli tloek ing a haiawh koep unawh kumqui ak hqing ce bawk uhy. A mimah a boei lumyk ce anih ak khanawh tloeng unawh:  
\v 11 Kaimih a Bawipa ingkaw Khawsa, thangleeknaak, kqihchahnaak ingkaw thaawmnaak ce nang ing na huh aham tyng qoe hy. Ikawtih nang ing soepkep boeih sai hyk ti, namah ak kawngaih amyihna cekkhqi ce sai tiksaw awm uhy,” ti uhy.   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Ezek. 2.9,10; Is. 29.11.\x*Cekcoengawh boei ngawih doelh awh ak ngawi thlang ak tang kut awh hatnaak khqih ak awm hu hai na a qee cazawl ce hu nyng.  
\v 2 Cawh tha ak awm thlang khan ceityih pynoet ing awi khawteh na, “Vawhkaw hatnaak ve hqe nawh cazawl ve u ing a hlam thai kaw?” tinawh khy hy.  
\v 3 Cawh khan ingkaw dek awh, dek ak kai nakaw cazawl hlam nawh ak khui dy ak toek hly u a ca pynoet awm am awm hy.  
\v 4 Cazawl hlam nawh ak khui ben ak toek hly kawi thlang pynoet awm ama awm a dawngawh kqang khing nyng.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Gen 49.9; \xt Is. 11.1,10.\x*Cawh a hqamca pynoet ing ka venawh, “Koeh kqang! Toek lah, Juda pa ak khuiawh kaw samthyyn, David Zung ing noeng hawh hy. Anih ing cazawl ingkaw hatnaak khqih ce awng thai hy,” tina hy.   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt Is. 53.7; \xt Zech. 4.10.\x*Cekcoengawh him ce a myihna ak awm tuuca pynoet, boei ngawihdoelh ang lung awh dyi nawh, ak hqing ik-oeih sai pupthli ingkaw mik khqih tahy, cekkhqi cetaw khawmdek awh a tyih Khawsang myihla khqih na awm hy.  
\v 7 Anih ing boei ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi thlang ak tang kut awhkaw cazawl ce lo hy.   
\p
\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Sam 141.2.\x*A lawh coengawh, ik-oeih sai ak hqing pupthli tloek ingkaw a hqamca a thong pupthli tloek ce Tuuca haiawh tlu unawh beek uhy. Cekkhqi ing tingtoeng ta qip unawh thlakciimkhqi a cykcahnaak bawktui ing ak be boet ce ta qip bai uhy.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt Sam 33.3; 98.1; Is. 42.10.\x*Cekkhqi ing lak thai ce sa uhy: Nang taw cazawl ingkaw hatnaak ce ak hlam aham kawih na qoe hyk ti, kawtih him na awm hawh tiksaw, na thi ing rampum ingkaw phynlum khui awhkaw thlangkhqi ce Khawsa hamna thlai hawh hyk ti.   
\p
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt Ex. 19.6; Awph 1.6.\x*Cemih thlangkhqi ce ram ingkaw ningnih a Khawsa a bibi aham khawsoeihkhqi na sai hawh hyk ti, ce mihkhqi ce khawmdek awh boei poe kawm uh,” tinawh sa uhy.   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt Dan. 7.10.\x*Ka toek awh khan ceityih khawzah thlang a thong thong ingkaw a sang sang ak awi ce za nyng. Cekkhqi ing ik-oeih sai ak hqing ingkaw a hqamcakhqi ing boei ngawihdoelh ce chung uhy.  
\v 12 Awi khawteh na: Him ce na ak awm Tuuca ing, thaawmnaak boeimangnaak ingkaw kqihchahnaak zoeksang naak ingkaw kyihcahnaak ce huh aham tyng qoe hy!” tinawh laa sa uhy.   
\p
\v 13 Cekcoengawh khan ingkaw dek, tuicun ingkaw ak khuiawh ak awm ik-oeih sai boeih ing laa sa uhy: “Boei ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi ingkaw Tuuca a venawh, kyihcahnaak, kqihchah naak, zoeksang naak ingkaw thaawmnaak kumqui dyna awm seh!” tinawh.  
\v 14 Ik-oeih sai ak hqing pupthli tloek ing, “Amen,” ti unawh a hqamcakhqi ing tluk doena bawk uhy.   
\c 6  
\p
\v 1 Tuuca ing hatnaak khqih ak khuiawh kaw lamma cyk hatnaak ce a hlam awh toek nyng. Cawh ik-oeih sai ak hqing pupthli ak khui awhkaw pynoet ing khawnghum awi amyihna khawteh na,: “Law!” ni tina hy.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Zech. 1.8; 6.3,6.\x*Ka toek awh, ka haiawh mirang bawk pynoet ce hu nyng! Ce mirang awh la ak pawm thlang pynoet ngawi hy, anih ce boei lumyk pe uhy, qaal noeng nawh noengnaak ing mirang awh ngawi hy.   
\p
\v 3 Tuuca ing a voeihih hatnaak ce awng tlaih bai hy, cawh ik-oeih sai ak hqing a pakkhihnaak ing, “Law!” ni tina hy.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 6:4 \xt Zech. 1.8; 6.2.\x*Cawh mai myihna ak sen mirang ak chang pynoet ce law hy. Ce a mirang awh ak ngawi cetaw khawmdek awhkaw qoepnaak lo valh nawh thlangkhqi pynoet ingkaw pynoet him saknaak ce pehy. Anih a venawh zawzik bau soeih pe uhy.   
\p
\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt Zech. 6.2,6.\x*Tuuca ing apak thum hatnaak ce am awng awh, ik-oeih sai ak hqing apak thumnaak ing, “Law!” a tice za nyng, ka toek awh ka haiawh mirang mym ce hu nyng! Ce mirang khanawh ak ngawi ing cawi tahnaak ce a kut awh pawm hy.  
\v 6 Cekcoengawh ik-oeih ak hqing pupthli anglakawhkaw awi ing, “Hypoet bibi phu ting sangvyt sum oet ingkaw nyn oet bibi phu ting barli sup thum, cekcoengawh situi ingkaw misur tui ce koeh plawci sak,” tinawh kqawn hy.   
\p
\v 7 Tuuca ing a pupthli hatnaak ce am awng awh, ik-oeih hqing a pupthlinaak ing, “Law!” a ti awh ce za nyng.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 6:8 \xt Ezek. 14.21.\x*Ka toek awh, ka haiawh a thi amak awm mirang ce hu nyng! Ce mirang awh ak ngawi cetaw Thihnaak mingna hy, ce a hu awh Hades ing hqut hy. Khawmdek awh ak awm thlang a hloep phlinaak ce zawzi ing him thainaak, khawseet khawkhanaak, ramsa tlung ing him thainaak ce cekqawi a venawh pehy.   
\p
\v 9 Hatnaak a pumhanaak ce am awng awh, Khawsak awi ing ce ak awi a ming dyihpyi a dawngawh bawkthang ak kaiawh thlang ing a him myihla ak awmkhqi ce hu nyng.  
\v 10 Cekkhqi ing awi khawteh na, Bawimang Khawsa, ak ciim ingkaw ak thym, khawmdek awh ak awmkhqi ve iqyt dy kaimih a thi phu kut thung nawh awi deng kaana na awm kaw?” tinawh khy uhy.   
\p
\v 11 Cekkhqi pynoet qip a venawh hik bawk ce pe unawh, kawlhkalh qeh aham ingkaw a mingmih a myihna him na ak awm thlangkhqi a cup hlan dy qeh aham kqawn pek khqi hy.   
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 6:12 \xt Awph 11.13; 16.18; \xt Is. 13.10; Joel 2.10,31; 3.15; Mat 24.29; Marka 13.24,25; Luke 21.25.\x*Hatnaak ak kquknaak am awng ce toek nyng. Cawh lipi khawteh na tat hy. Me a myi ing a tah tlamhi a myihna khawmik ce mym zur hy, thi a myihna pihla awm thim hy,  
\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt Is. 34.4.\x*Thai thaih khawhli ing thloek nawh ang kqi a myihna khan nakawng aihchikhqi ce dek na tla hy.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 6:14 \xt Awph 16.20.\x*Khawk khawnghi ce canhah a myihna zawl qu nawh, tlangkhqi ingkaw sanglakkhqi awm thoek kang hy.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 6:15 \xt Is. 2.19,21.\x*Cawh khawmdek awhkaw sangpahrang khqi, sangpahrang cakhqi, qalboeikhqi, boeikhqi, tha ak awm thlangkhqi, tamnaakhqi ingkaw ak loetkhqi ce tlang awh ak awm lungnuk khuikhqi awh thuk uhy.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Hos. 10.8; Luke 23.30.\x*Tlangkhqi ingkaw lungnukhqi venawh, Ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi a haai ingkaw Tuuca ak kawsonaak chungdah aham kaimih ve nng cuuk sih khqi lah!  
\v 17 \x - \xo 6:17 \xt Joel 2.11; Mal. 3.2.\x*Vekkhqi ak kawsonaak khawnghi pui taw pha law hawh hy, u ing a yh thai kaw?” tinawh khy uhy.   
\c 7  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 7:1 \xt Jer. 49.36; Dan. 7.2; Zech. 6.5.\x*Cekcoengawh taw khawmdek kil pupphli awh ak pha law khan ceityih pupthli ce hu nyng, cekkhqi ing dek khan, tuicun ingkaw thingkhqi awh awm ama hlinaak aham khawmdek awh zilh pupthli ce tu khak uhy.  
\v 2 Cekcoengawh khawlaw benna kawng ak law khan ceityih pynoet ce hu bai nyng, anih ing ak hqing Khawsa hatnaak ce tahy. Dek ingkaw tuicun plawci sak thainaak ak ta khan ceityih pupthli ce anih ing khawteh na khy hy:  
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt Ezek. 9.4,6.\x*Khawsa a tyihzoeihkhqi a talri awh hatnaak ka taak peek hlan dy dek ingkaw tuicun ingkaw thingkhqi ce koeh plawci sak,” tina hy.   
\p
\v 4 Cekcoengawh hatnaak ak takhqi noetnaak ce za nyng: Isarael pilnam boeih khui awhkawng 144, 000 law hy.   
\li1
\v 5 Juda pilnam khuiawh 12,000 hatnaak tahy,  
\li1 Reuben pilnam khuiawh 12,000,  
\li1 Gad pilnam khuiawh 12,000,   
\li1
\v 6 Asher pilnam khuiawh 12,000,  
\li1 Naphtali pilnam khuiawh 12,000,  
\li1 Manasseh pilnam khuiawh 12,000,   
\li1
\v 7 Simeon pilnam khuiawh 12,000,  
\li1 Levi pilnam khuiawh 12,000,  
\li1 Assachar pilnam khuiawh 12,000,   
\li1
\v 8 Zebulun pilnam khuiawh 12,000,  
\li1 Joseph pilnam khuiawh 12,000,  
\li1 Bejamin pilnam khuiawh 12,000  
\m tloek ve hanta awm hy.  
\v 9 Cekcoengawh ka toek awh, qamtawm, phynlum, awi cawm awi ce u ingawm ama noet noeng thlang kqeng boei ngawihdoelh ingkaw Tuuca haiawh ak dyi ce hu nyng. Cekkhqi ing hik bawk ce bai unawh ami kut samtoe ce pawm uhy.  
\v 10 Awi khawteh na: Hulnaak taw boei ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi ningnih a Khawsa ingkaw Tuuca a koe ni,” tinawh khy uhy.   
\p
\v 11 Khan ceityih boeih ing boei ngawihdoelh ing a hqamcakhqi ingkaw ik-oeih sai hqing pupthli tloek ce chung unawh dyi uhy. Boei ngawihdoelh haiawh koep doena Khawsa ce bawk uhy,  
\v 12 ve myihna kqawn uhy: “Amen! Kyihcahnaak, zoeksangnaak, cyihnaak ingkaw zeel awi kqawnnaak, kqihchahnaak, saithainaak, thaawmnaak taw kumqui dyna ningnih a Khawsa ni Amen,” ti uhy.   
\p
\v 13 Cawh a hqamca pynoet ing ni doet hy, “Vawhkaw hik bawk ak baikhqi ve u khqi nu, hana kawng ami law?” ni tina hy.   
\p
\v 14 \x - \xo 7:14 \xt Dan. 12.1; Mat 24.21; Marka 13.19.\x*Kai ing, “Bawipa namah ing sim hyk ti,” tina nyng. Cawh anih ing, “Vawhkaw thlangkhqi vetaw kyinaak ak bau soeih khui awhkawng ak law khqi ni, Tuuca thi ingkaw a hikhqi ce ak bawk cana ak chuk thlangkhqi ni.  
\v 15 Cedawngawh, cekkhqi taw Khawsa a ngawihdoelh a haiawh awm unawh than dai a bawkim khuiawh a bi ce bi pe uhy, boei ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi ing cekkhqik khanawh hi im ce zyng pek khqi kaw.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 7:16 \xt Is. 49.10.\x*Buh am cawi qoe voel kawm uh, tui awm am ngaih voel kawm uh, khawling ing am eng khqi voel kawmsaw, a ling ingawm am dawi thai voel kaw.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 7:17 \xt Sam 23.1; Ezek. 34.23; \xt Sam 23.2; Is. 49.10; \xt Is. 25.8.\x*Kawtih boei ngawihdoelh ang lung awh ak ngawi Tuuca ce cekkhqi a tuukhaikung na awm kawmsaw hqingnaak tui a lawngnaak kung awh cekkhqi ce sawi khqi kaw. A mikphli tuikhqi ce Khawsa ing huih pek khqi kaw,” tina hy.   
\c 8  
\p
\v 1 Hatnaak ak khqihnaak ce am awng awh, khan na khawnoek keekvang khui a dinkqak na awm hy.  
\v 2 Cawh Khawsa haiawh ak dyi khan ceityih khqih ce hu nyng, cekkhqi venawh uut khqih pek khqi hy.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 8:3 \xt Amos 9.1; \xt Ex. 30.1,3.\x*Khan ceityih ak chang pynoet, bawktui bawm pawm doena law nawh bawkthang a haiawh ce dyi hy. Thlakciimkhqi a cykcahnaak ce boei ngawihdoelh a haiawh ak awm sui bawkthang awh nawn aham bawktui khawzah ce anih a venawh pe uhy.  
\v 4 Bawktui ingkaw thlakciimkhqi ak cykcahnaak ce khan ceityih kut awhkawng Khawsa haina hang kai hy.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 8:5 \xt Lev. 16.12; Ezek. 10.2; \xt Ex. 19.16; Awph 11.19; 16.18.\x*Cekcoengawh khan ceityih ing bawktui bawm ce lo nawh, bawkthang awhkaw mai ce ahawk sih coengawh dek awh hawk hy; cekcoengawh khawnghum awi, khawkphla ingkaw khawmdek awh lipi ce tat hy.  
\v 6 Uut ak pawm khan ceityih khqih ing uut ce yng uhy.   
\p
\v 7 \x - \xo 8:7 \xt Ex. 9.23-25; Ezek. 38.22.\x*Ak lamma cyk khan ceityih ing uut ce yng hy, cawh rel ingkaw thi ing ak kqit qu mai ce dek awh hawk qu hy. Cawh khawmdek hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet, thing hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet ingkaw sai ak hqingkhqi boeih ce ui hy.   
\p
\v 8 A pak khihnaak khan ceityih ing uut ce a yng awh, tlang ak bau soeih amyihna ak awm ik-oeih pynoet ce mai awh ui nawh tuicun na khawng qu hy. Cawh tuicun hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet ce thi na thoeng hy,  
\v 9 tuicun khuiawh ak hqing ik-oeih hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet ce thi nawh, tui awh ak cet lawng hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet te plawci kang hy.   
\p
\v 10 \x - \xo 8:10 \xt Is. 14.12.\x*Apak thumnaak khan ceityih ing uut ce a yng awh, khan nakawng maihchoei a myihna ak kqawng aihchi ak bau soeih ce tuiva ingkaw lawngca hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet awh nung tla hy –  
\v 11 \x - \xo 8:11 \xt Jer. 9.15.\x*cawhkaw aihchi cetaw Thikkha mingna hy. Tui hloep thum awh hloep oet ce kha sak hy, cawhkaw tuihkha ami awk a dawngawh thlang khawzah ing thi hy.   
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 8:12 \xt Is. 13.10; Ezek. 32.7; Joel 2.10,31; 3.15.\x*A pupthlinaak khan ceityih ing uut ce a yng awh, khawmik hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet, pihla hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet, aihchi hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet ce than hy. Khawkdai hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet ce vangnaak am awm nawh than hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet awm vangnaak am awm hy.  
\v 13 Ka toek awh, khan khawnghi zilh awh ak ding awi khawteh na ak khy huu pynoet ce hu nyng: “Khaw map hy! Khaw map hy! Ak chang khan ceityih pakthum ing uut yng aham a awm hyn a dawngawh khawmdek awh ak thlangkhqi ham khaw map hy!” tinawh khy hy.   
\c 9  
\p
\v 1 Khan ceityih a pumhanaak ing uut ce yng hy, cawh khan nakawng dek awh anuk tla law aihchi pynoet ce hu nyng. Cawhkaw aihchi venawh a dytnaak amak awm lawk-kqawng dung cabi ce pe uhy.  
\v 2 Anih ing a dytnaak amak awm lawk-kqawng dung ce am awng awh, mai ak cak soeih maikhu amyihna maikhu ce hang thoeng law hy. Khawmik ingkaw khawhli boeih ce a dytnaak amak awm lawk-kqawng awh maikhu ing than sak hy.  
\v 3 Cawhkaw maikhu awhkawng khawmdek awh khamkhawkkhqi ce law unawh cekkhqi venawh khawmdek awhkaw cengta-ai amyihna saithainaak ce pehy.  
\v 4 Khawmdek awh sai, thingling ingkaw thingkhqi ama plawci sak aham cekkhqi venawh awipeeknaak awm hlai hy, a talqi awh Khawsa hatnaak amak awmkhqi ce plawci sak aham awi pehy.  
\v 5 Cekkhqi him thainaak taw am pe nawh hla nga ak khui kyinaak ingkaw thekhanaak peek aham awi pehy. Cawhkaw khuikha huhnaak cetaw cengta-ai ing thlang ak cep awhkaw amyihna tlo hy.  
\v 6 Cemyihna a awm ak khuiawh thlangkhqi ing thihnaak ce sui hlai voei uh, am hu kawm uh; thih hy hlai voei uh thihnaak ing cekkhqi ce centaak khqi kaw.  
\v 7 Cawhkaw khamkhawkkhqi cetaw qaal tuk aham oepchoeh na ak awm meqangkhqi amyihna awm uhy. A lu awh sui lumyk amyihna ak awm lumyk ce myk qip uhy, ami haaikhqi taw thlanghqing a haai amyihna awm hy.  
\v 8 Ami lusamkhqi taw nukhqi a lusam amyihna awm nawh, ami hakhqi taw samthyyn a hakhqi amyihna awm hy.  
\v 9 Thi amyihna ak awm kqangdan bai unawh, ang hla ang hum awi taw qaal tuknaak awh ak dawng meqang khawzah ak awi amyihna awm hy.  
\v 10 A ming maikhqi awm nawh cengta-ai amyihna thlang cep hy, ang mai ing hla nga ak khui thlang kyinaak pe thai hy.  
\v 11 A dytnaak amak awm lawk-kqawng dung khuiawh kaw khan ceityih ce a mingmih a sangpahrang na ta uhy, anih ang ming taw Abaddon mingna hy, Greek awi na taw Apollyon mingna hy.  
\v 12 Lamma awhkaw khaw mapnaak taw khum hawh hy; cehlai khaw mapnaak pakkhih ce a law aham awm hyn hy.   
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 9:13 \xt Ex. 30.1-3.\x*Ak kquknaak khan ceityih ing uut ce a yng awh, Khawsa haiawh ak awm sui bawkthang awhkaw kii awhkawng awi ce za nyng.  
\v 14 Ce ing uut ak pawm khan ceityih a venawh, “Euphrates long awh pin na ak awm khan ceityih tloek ce hlah hlah,” tina hy.  
\v 15 Ve khawnoek, nyn, hla ingkaw kum aham qoe qoe na a pin khan ceityih pupthli tloek ce dek thlang hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet him aham hlah hy.  
\v 16 Mirang awh ak ngawi cawhkaw qalkap cetaw million zanhih law hy. Cekkhqi izah ami law tice za nyng.  
\v 17 Mirangkhqi ingkaw meqang ak khanawh ak ngawi thlangkhqi ce vemyihna hu nyng: Amik kqangdankhqi ce maikqawng amyihna ak hlawk, nukzup na ak awm ingkaw kat amyihna ak engkhqi na awm hy. Mirangkhqi cetaw samthyyn a lukhqi amyihna awm nawh am kha awhkawng maikqawng, maikhu ingkaw kat ce thoeng hy.  
\v 18 Cekkhqi am khak khui awhkawng ak thoeng nat pakthum maikqawng, maikhu ingkaw kat ing khawmdek awh thlang hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet ce him hy.  
\v 19 Ce meqangkhqi a saithainaak taw ang mai ingkaw am kha awh awm hy; ang maikhqi ce khqui amyihna a lu awm nawh thlang ngawha ai sak hy.  
\v 20 Vawhkaw nat ing am him nawh ak ngen tloek ce a mimah a kutsai awh zut hlan bak bak uhy; qaai bawk unawh, sui, ngun qawhum lung thing ing sai uhy- a mik amak dang, awi am za thai nawh amak cet thai myiqawlkhqi bawknaak ce am qoeng bak bak uhy.  
\v 21 Thlang himnaak, miklet, kutlam toeknaak, nu pa thawlh sainaak ingkaw quuk am qaainaak awh am zut bak bak uhy.   
\c 10  
\p
\v 1 Cekcoengawh khan nakawng a nuk kqum law tha ak awm soeih khan ceityih ak chang pynoet ce hu nyng. Myi ce hi na bai nawh, a lu sawawh thlimha ce awm hy; a haai taw khawmik amyihna awm nawh a khaw qawi taw maihtung amyihna awm hy.  
\v 2 A kut awh cazawl tehca ce pawm nawh a kut awh phaih hy. Tang ben a khaw ing tuicun leh nawh cawng ben a khaw ing dek leh hy,  
\v 3 samthyyn kawk awi amyihna khawteh na a nih ce khy hy. Ak khy awh, khawnghum khqih ing awi kqawn hy.  
\v 4 Khawnghum khqih ing awi ak kqawn awh, ca qee aham cai nyng; cehlai khan benna kaw awi ing, “Khawnghum khqih ing awi ak kqawn ce koeh qee nawhtaw hatnaak ta lah,” ni tina hy.   
\p
\v 5 \x - \xo 10:5 \xt Ex. 20.11; Deut. 32.40; Dan. 12.7; Amos 3.7.\x*Tui ingkaw dek awh ak dyi khan ceityih ing ak tang ben kut ce khan na hak thlek hy.  
\v 6 Kumqui dy ak hqing, khan ingkaw ak khuiawh ak awm ik-oeihkhqi boeih ak saikung, dek ingkaw ak khuiawh ak awm ik-oeihkhqi boeih ak saikung, ang ming ing awi sa hy, “Am yih voel kaw!  
\v 7 Cehlai ak khqihnaak khan ceityih ing uut yng vang a ti awh, Khawsa a koe ang hyp ik-oeih ce amah a tyihzawih tawnghakhqi venawh ak kqawn peek oepchoeh amyihna soep hawh kaw,” tinawh kqawn hy.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 10:8 \xt Ezek. 2.8—3.3.\x*Cekcoengawh khan benna kaw kang zaak awi ing awi ti law tlaih bai hy: “Cet nawhtaw, tuicun ingkaw dek awh ak dyi khan ceityih a kut awh a phaih cazawl ce lo lah,” ni tina hy.   
\p
\v 9 Cedawngawh cawhkaw khan ceityih a venna cet nyng saw cazawl ce thoeh nyng. Anih ing, “Lo nawhtaw ai lah. Nak phoen ak khuina thui hlai voei, nam kha awhtaw khawi amyihna awi kaw,” ni tina hy.  
\v 10 Khan ceityih a kut awhkaw cazawl ce lo nyng saw ai nyng. Kam kha awh khawi amyihna awi hy, cehlai ka ai coeng awhtaw kak phoen khuina thui hy.  
\v 11 Cawh, Thlang khawzah, qamtawn, phynlum ingkaw sangpahrangkhqi venawh awi kqawn tlaih kawp ti,” ni tina hy.   
\c 11  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 11:1 \xt Ezek. 40.3; Zech. 2.1,2.\x*Caityng a myihna ak awm thikdyng pynoet ce ani peek coengawh, “Cet nawhtaw Khawsa a tempul ingkaw bawkthang ce tah lah, cekcoengawh vawh Khawsa ak beek thlangkhqi ce toek lah.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 11:2 \xt Luke 21.24.\x*Cehlai a leng ben taw koeh pa sak; koeh tah, cetaw Gentelkhqi hamna ni. Cekkhqi ing khawk bau ciim ce nyn 42 khui khaw ing leh kawm uh.  
\v 3 Cekcoengawh kai ing ka mah a dyihthing thlang pakkhih a venawh saithainaak pe kawng nyng saw cekqawi ing tlamhi bai kawm nihsaw, khawnghi 1260 khui awi kqawn kawm nih,” ni tina hy.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 11:4 \xt Zech. 4.3,11-14.\x*Vekkqawi vetaw khawmdek Bawi a haiawh ak dyi olive thing pakkhih ingkaw mai vangnaak pakkhih na awm hy.  
\v 5 U ingawm cekqawi ce tlawhnat sak aham a ngaih awhtaw, am khak khui awhkawng maikqawng ce thoeng sak nih nawh a qaalkhqi ce daih hy nih. U awm cekqawi ce tlawhnat sak aham ak ngaih taw cemyihna ce thi kaw.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 11:6 \xt 1 Kin. 17.1; \xt Ex. 7.17-19; \xt 1 Sam. 4.8.\x*Awi ani phawng khuiawh awm ama aanaak aham khan chawh ce khai hy nih; tui awm thi na thoeng sak thai nih nawh ani ngaihnaak a myihna khawmdek awh tlawhnat soepkep ce law sak thai hy nih.   
\p
\v 7 \x - \xo 11:7 \xt Dan. 7.7; Awph 13.5-7; 17.8; \xt Dan. 7.21.\x*Cekkqawi ing awi anik kqawn boet coeng awhtaw, a dytnaak amak awm lawk-kqawng dung khuiawh kawng ak thoeng law ramsa tlung ing cekqawi ce tuk kaw, noeng kawmsaw cekqawi ce him kaw.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 11:8 \xt Is. 1.9,10.\x*Cekkqawi a pum ce khawk bau awhkaw lam awh helh hyt kawm uh, cawhkaw khawk bau ce ikaw mih nu ti kqawn nytnaak na Sodom ingkaw Izip tinawh khy uhy, cawh cekqawi a Bawipa awm thinglam awh ana tai uhy.  
\v 9 Khaw nyn thum coengawh kekvang thlang tawm, phynlum, awi cawm awi ce ing qampum awhkaw thlangkhqi ing mikkel ing qym kawm usaw cekqawi a qawk ce vui aham thana kawm uh.  
\v 10 Cawhkaw tawngha qawi ing khawmdek awh ak awm thlangkhqi ce ana thekhanaak hawh a dawngawh thlangkhqi ing cekqawi ak khanawh zeel kawm usaw pynoet ingkaw pynoet kutdo ik-oeih pat qu kawm uh.   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 11:11 \xt Ezek. 37.10.\x*Cehlai nyn thum coengawh kengvang a awm coeng awhtaw cekqawi ing Khawsa venna kaw hqingnaak hqi ce hu tlaih nih nawh ani khaw ing dyi hy nih, cawh ak hukhqi ing kqih uhy.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 11:12 \xt 2 Kin. 2.11.\x*Cawh khan benna kawng awi khawteh na, “Hang law lah,” a ti awi ce za hy nih. A qaalkhqi ing ami toek huili awh khan khawnghi myi awh hang kai hy nih.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 11:13 \xt Awph 6.12; 16.18.\x*Cawh lipi khawteh na tat nawh khawk bau hloep hra khuiawh hloep oet ce plawci hy. Thlang thong khqih ce lipi a dawngawh thi uhy, a mik awm tloek ce ly unawh khan Khawsa ce zoeksang uhy.  
\v 14 Khaw map pak khihnaak ce khum nawh, khaw map apak thumnaak ce a law aham awm hy.   
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 11:15 \xt Ex. 15.18; Dan. 2.44; 7.14,27.\x*Khan ceityih ak khqihnaak ing uut ce a yng awh, khan na awi khawteh na qeng hy, cawhkaw awi ing, “Khawmdek ram ve ningnih Bawipa ingkaw a Khrih a ram na coeng hawh hy, anih ing kumqui dy uk hawh kaw,” tihy.   
\p
\v 16 Cekcoengawh Khawsa haiawh kaw boei ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi a hqamca a thong pupthli tloek ing koep unawh Khawsa ce beek uhy:   
\p
\v 17 Bawimang soeih soeih Bawipa Khawsa, na venawh zeelnaak awi kqawn law u nyng, nang taw ak awm huili ingkaw ak awm coeng hawh na awm hyk ti, na sai ik-oeih bau soeih ce lo tiksaw boei na ngawi hawh hyk ti.   
\p
\v 18 \x - \xo 11:18 \xt Sam 2.5; 110.5; \xt Sam 115.13.\x*Rampum awhkaw thlangkhqi ce amik kaw so unawh nang ak kawsonaak ce pha law hy, thlakthikhqi awi dengnaak a tym ce pha law nawh, na tyihzoeihkhqi, na tawnghakhqi, nak thlakciimkhqi ingkaw nang ming ak kqihchah thlangkhqi, thlak zawi, thlak bau aham kutdo huhnaak tym ce pha law hawh hy, khawmdek ak hqe thlangkhqi hqenaak nyn ce pha law hawh hy,” tinawh kqawn hy.   
\p
\v 19 \x - \xo 11:19 \xt Awph 8.5; 16.18; \xt Awph 16.21.\x*Cekcoengawh taw khanna ak awm Khawsa a tempul ce awng qu nawh, cawhkaw tempul khuiawh paipi a sainaak bawm ce awm hy, ce a nyn awhkawng kqek mai ing, khawnghum awi ing, lipi tat nawh kqek khawzah ce kqi hy.   
\c 12  
\p
\v 1 Kawpoek kyinaak bau soeih khanna dang hy: khawmik ce hi na bai nawh a khaw awh pihla ak ta a lu awh aihchi pahqa hlaihih ak awm boei lumyk ak myk nu pynoet hu nyng.  
\v 2 Ce nu cetaw tat tloei na awm nawh naa awm vang a ti dawngawh tlo nawh khy hy.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 12:3 \xt Dan. 7.7.\x*Cawh khanna hatnaak ak chang pynoet awm bai hy: A lu khqih law nawh ak kii pahqa ak law, a lu awh boei lumyk khqih ak awm thlim ak thim ak bau soeih pynoet ce awm hy.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 12:4 \xt Dan. 8.10.\x*Ang mai ing khanna ak awm aihchi hloep thum khuiawh hloep oet ce khawi baat nawh dek na nuk khawng hy. Naa a awm awh daih pahoei vang tinawh cawhkaw thlim ce naa ak awm tawm nu a haiawh dyi hy.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 12:5 \xt Is. 66.7; \xt Sam 2.9.\x*Cawhkaw nu ing thi boeng ing rampum ak uk hly kawi a ca pa ce cuun hy. Ce a ca pa ce Khawsa ing a ngawihdoelh a awmnaak hun na pawm qu valh hy.  
\v 6 Ce nu ce Khawsa ing qoek abah pehy, qamkoh awh khawnghi 1,260 khui doeng khoemdoen aham dawng hy.   
\p
\v 7 \x - \xo 12:7 \xt Dan. 10.13,21; 12.1; Juda 1.9.\x*Cawh khan na qaal tuknaak awm hy. Mikael ingkaw ak khan ceityihkhqi ing thlim ce tuk uhy, thlim ingkaw khan ceityihkhqi ingawm tuk lawt uhy.  
\v 8 Cehlai cekkhqi ce amik tha ama awm a dawngawh khawk khan na awmnaak hun am ta thai voel hy.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 12:9 \xt Gen 3.1; \xt Luke 10.18.\x*Khawmdek pum ak ceh pyi thawlh qaai am awhtaw Setan khqui kqym thlim ce nuk thla uhy. Anih ce ak khan ceityihkhqi ing dek na nuk thlak khqi hy.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 12:10 \xt Job 1.9-11; Zech. 3.1.\x*Cawh khawk khan na khawteh na: “Tuh taw thawlhnaak ingkaw thaawmnaak ningnih Khawsa a ram ingkaw Khrih a saithainaak ce law hawh hy. Kawtih ningnih a koeinaakhqi thawlh ak pukkung, than dai ningnih Khawsa haiawh cekkhqi thawlh ak pukkung ce nuk thla law hawh uhy.  
\v 11 Tuucakhqi ingkaw awiphawngnaak ing anih ce noeng hawh uhy, thihnaak awhkawng qoeng aham cekkhqi ing a hqingnaak ce am lungna soeih uhy.  
\v 12 Cedawngawh nangmih khankhqi ingkaw ak khuiawh ak awm thlangkhqi, zeel lah uh! cehlai qaai ce nang a venna a nuk thlak law na a awm hawh a dawngawh, khawmdek ingkaw tuicun taw khaw map hyk ti. A tym tawica doeng ni a taak hawh tice a sim a dawngawh, anih ce ak kaw so hy,” tinawh awi ce za nyng.   
\p
\v 13 Khawmdek awh nuk khawng law na awm hawh nyng tice thlim ing a sim awh, nu pa ca ak cuun ce hquut hy.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 12:14 \xt Dan. 7.25; 12.7.\x*Cehlai ce a nu ce kawlhkalh toeknaak aham qoek abah pe hyt hy. Kqui ing ama phanaak qamkoh pynoet awh a tym iqyt nu, a tym kekvang khuiawh ding thainaak aham huu ak bau soeih ang hla qawi ce pe uhy.  
\v 15 Kqui ing am kha khuiawh kawng long tui amyihna tui sa nawh cawhkaw tui ak tha ing nu ce ban aham cai hy.  
\v 16 Cehlai khawmdek ing ce a nu ce hul hy, khqui ing am kha khuiawh kawng long tui amyihna a sa tui ce khawmdek ang nawh daih pe boeih hy.  
\v 17 Cawh thlim ce nu ak khanawh ak kaw so hy, Khawsa ak awipeek ngaih nawh Jesu ak awih kqawn ak tu ce nu a cadilkhqi ing tuk qu aham cet hy.   
\c 13  
\p
\v 1 Thlim ce tuicun keng awh dyi hy. Cawh tuicun khui awhkawng ak thoeng law qamsatlung ce hu nyng. Cawhkaw qamsatlung cetaw ak kii pahqa ingkaw a lu khqih tahy, ak kii boeih awh boei lumyk pahqa awm hy, a lu boeih awh Khawsa kqawn seetnaak ming awm boeih hy.  
\v 2 Cawhkaw qamsatlung ka huh cetaw kaityn ing lo qu hy nih. Cehlai a khaw taw phawm a khaw amyihna awm nawh am kha taw samthyyn am kha amyihna awm hy. Thlim ing cawhkaw qamsatlung a venawh thaawmnaak, boei ngawihdoelh ingkaw saithainaak ak bau soeih ce pehy.  
\v 3 A lu pynoet taw ngawha ai hlai hy, ngawha a ai ce qoei hawh hy. Khawmdek pum amik kawpoek kyi nawh cawhkaw qamsatlung a hu awh bat uhy.  
\v 4 Qamsatlung a venawh saithainaak ce a peek a dawngawh thlangkhqi ing thlim ce bawk uhy, qamsatlung awm bawk unawh, “U nu qamsatlung amyihna ak awm? U ing anih ve a tuk thai kaw?” ti uhy.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 13:5 \xt Dan. 7.8,25; 11.36.\x*Oeknaak ingkaw Khawsa thekhanaak awi kqawn aham hui am lai ingkaw, hla 42 khui amah ngaih ik-oeih saithainaak ce pe uhy.  
\v 6 Anih ing Khawsa kqawn seet aham ingkaw anih ang ming ing anih a awmnaak hun ingkaw khan awh ak awm thlangkhqi boeih kqawn seet aham am kha ce awng hy.  
\v 7 Thlakciimkhqi tuk thainaak ingkaw noeng thainaak ce hu hy. Phynlum, thlangtawm, awi cawm awi ce ingkaw qampum ak khanawh saithainaak ce tahy.  
\v 8 Khawmdek a syn cyk awh ami him tuuca a hqingnaak cauk ak khuiawh ang ming qee na amak awm khawmdek thlangkhqi boeih ing cawhkaw qamsatlung ce bawk kawm uh.  
\v 9 U awm zaaknaak haa ak ta ingtaw za seh.   
\p
\v 10 \x - \xo 13:10 \xt Jer. 15.2; 43.11.\x*Tamnaa na ak khum hly kawi thlang taw tamnaa na khum kaw. Zawzi ing him hly kawi thlang taw zawzi ing him na awm kaw. Cedawngawh thlakciimkhqi ing kawdung doena yhnaak taak aham ingkaw ypawm na awm aham ngoe hy.   
\p
\v 11 Cedawngawh khawmdek awhkaw ak law qamsatlung pynoet ce hu nyng. Tuuca amyihna kii pakkhih ta hlai hy, thlim amyihna awi pau hy.  
\v 12 Lamma awhkaw qamsatlung ang zyngna anih a saithainaakkhqi boeih boeih ce sai nawh ngawha ak ai nawh ak qoei hawh lamma awhkaw qamsatlung ce dek awhkawng thlang boeih bawk sak hy.  
\v 13 Anih ing kawpoek kyi hatnaak ik-oeihkhqi ce sai hy, thlang a mik huh awh khawk khan nakawng pateng za mai nung tlak law sak hy.  
\v 14 Lamma awhkaw qamsatlung ang zyngna hatnaakkhqi saithainaak ce a venawh peek na a awm a dawngawh, khawmdek awh ak awm thlangkhqi ce anih ing thai nahy. Zawzi ing ngawha ai hlai hy ak hqing tlaih qamsatlung kqihchahnaak myiqawl sai aham anih ing awi pehy.  
\v 15 Cawhkaw myiqawl bawk aham ak thanaak thlang boeih ce him saknaak thai awi kqawn aham lamma awhkaw qamsatlung myiqawl hqi sak thainaak ce anih a venawh peek na awm hy.  
\v 16 Thlang boeih, ak zawi ak bau, boei ingkaw khawdeng, ak loet ingkaw tamnaa cawng kut benawh am awhtaw a talqi awh hatnaak boeih anih ing taak sak ngah ngah hy,  
\v 17 cedawngawh qamsatlung ang ming am awhtaw ang ming a nambat hatnaak amak ta ingtaw ik-oeih am zawi thai kawmsaw thlai awm am thlai thai kawm uh.  
\v 18 Ve ing cyihnaak ngoe hy, u ingawm ak poek thai awhtaw qamsa a nambat ce noet lah seh, kawtih vawhkaw nambat taw thlanghqing nambat na awm hy, anih a nambat taw 666 na awm hy.   
\c 14  
\p
\v 1 Tuuca ingkaw 144,000, cekcoengawh ka toek hlai, ka haiawh tuuca, zion tlang awh ak dyi ce hu nyng, anih ang ming ing a pa ang ming a talqi awh ak qee thlang 144,000 a venawh ak awm ce hu hy.  
\v 2 Cawh khawk khan nakawng tuilet awi ingkaw khawnghum awi amyihna za nyng. Cawhkaw awi cetaw tingtoeng ak tumkhqi ing tingtoeng ami tum awhkaw amyihna awm hy.  
\v 3 Cekkhqi ing boei ngawihdoelh a haai ingkaw ik-oeih sai ak hqing pupthli a haai ingkaw a hqamcakhqi haiawh lak thai ce sa uhy. Khawmdek awh thaawng na ak awm thlang 144,000 doeng am ingtaw u ingawm ce a laa ce am sa thai hy.  
\v 4 Vekkhqi vetaw nu ingqawi am thawlh nawh ak ciimcaih na ak awm thlangkhqi na awm uhy. Cekkhqi ing Tuuca a cehnaak hoei awh hquut uhy. Cekkhqi cetaw thlangkhqing lak awhkawng ak thlaih thlangkhqi na awm unawh Khawsa ingkaw Tuuca venawh thaihcyk nawn na awm uhy.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 14:5 \xt Zeph. 3.13.\x*A hui awm qaai am awm nawh; coet amak kap thlangkhqi na awm uhy.   
\p
\v 6 Cekcoengawh khan khawnghi awh ak ding khan ceityih ak chang pynoet ce hu nyng, anih ing khawmdek awh ak awm qampum, phynlum ingkaw awi cawm awi ce thlangkhqi venawh phawng aham kumqui awithang leek ce tahy.  
\v 7 Anih ing khawteh na, “Amah a awi dengnaak tym ce a pha law hawh a dawngawh, Khawsa ce kqih unawh thangleeknaak ce pe lah uh. Khan ingkaw dek, tuicun ingkaw lawngca ak saikung ce bawk lah uh,” tinawh khy hy.  
\v 8 Apak khihnaak khan ceityih ing, “Tlu hawh hy, qampum samphaih qawnaak misur tui ak awk sak Babylon khawk bau taw tlu hawh hy,” tinawh kqawn bai hy.  
\v 9 Apak thumnaak khan ceityih ing khawteh na, “U ingawm qamsatlung ingkaw a myiqawl ce bawk nawh a talqi awh am awhtaw a kut awh aw anih a hatnaak ak hu taw,  
\v 10 \x - \xo 14:10 \xt Is. 51.17; \xt Gen 19.24; Ezek. 38.22.\x*Khawsa ing ak kawsonaak boet awh thaawmnaak ak be na tloeih hy, kawsonaak misur tui ce aw lawt kaw. Tuuca ingkaw ak khan ceityih ciimkhqi haiawh cekkhqi ce kat mai ing dawi kaw.  
\v 11 A mingmih dawinaak kat maikhu ce kumqui dy boet qoe kaana khu kaw. Qamsatlung ingkaw a myiqawl ak bawk anih ang ming hatnaak ak hu thlangkhqi hamna than dai dymnaak qoe qoe am awm kaw,” tinawh khy hy.  
\v 12 Ve dawngawh Khawsak awipeek ngai nawh Jesu awh ypawm na ak awm thlakciimkhqi ing kawdung naak ing yh aham ngoe hy.  
\v 13 Cekcoengawh khan benna kawng awi pynoet za nyng, “Ree lah: Tuh kawng Bawipa awh ak thi thlangkhqi taw ami zoseen hy.” “Oeih, a bibinaak awhkawng dym kawm usaw, a bibinaak ing a mingmih ce hquut hawh lawt kaw,” tinawh Myihla ing kqawn hy.   
\p
\v 14 Ka toek awh, ka haiawh myiqawl awm a bawk awm nawh, cawhkaw myiqawl a bawk awh ak ngawi cetaw, “Thlanghqing Capa” na awm nawh, a lu awh sui lumyk myk nawh a kut awh vin ak hqat ce pawm hy.  
\v 15 Khan ceityih ak chang pynoet ce bawkim khuiawh kawng law nawh myiqawl awh ak ngawi thlang a venawh khawteh na, “Na vin ce lo nawh aat hlah, cang ah ty khoek hawh hy, khawmdek awh cang hin boeih hawh hy,” tina hy.  
\v 16 Myiqawl awh ak ngawi thlang ing a vin ce dek na nuk hawi law hy, cawh dek ce aat hy.   
\p
\v 17 Khan na ak awm bawkim khui awhkawng khan ceityih pynoet ce law hy, anih ingawm vin ak hqat pynoet pawm hy.  
\v 18 Khan ceityih pynoet bai ce mai pawm law nawh bawkthang a venawh kawng law hy, awi khawteh na vin ak hqat ak pawm a venawh, “Na vin hqat ce lo nawh khawmdek awhkaw misur bawm ce aat hlah, misur thaih hin hawh hy,” tina hy.  
\v 19 Cawhkaw khan ceityih ing a vin ce khawmdek na nuk hawi hy, misur thaih bawm ce aat nawh Khawsa ak kawsonaak misur tui suinaak awh nuk khawng hy.  
\v 20 Khawk bau ceng awhkaw misur tui suinaak awh cawhkaw misur thaih bawm ce khaw ing leh uhy, cawhkaw a tui suinaak awhkawng thi lawng nawh meqang am khakkho dy a mylh na stadia 1,600 dy lawng hy.   
\c 15  
\p
\v 1 Khawk khan na kawpoek kyi hatnaak ak bau soeih ce hu nyng: khan ceityih khqih ingkaw tlawhche a dytnaak khqih dy awm hy, ce a ik-oeih dawngawh Khawsa ak kawsonaak ce soep hy.   
\p
\v 2 Mai ing ak kqit qu hlalang tuili amyihna ak awm ik-oeih ce hu nyng, cawhkaw tuili kengawh qamsatlung, a myiqawl ingkaw ang ming ak khanawh ak awm nambat ak cheiawh noengnaak ak ta thlangkhqi ce dyi uhy. Khawsa ing a peek tingtoeng ce cekkhqi ing pawm unawh,  
\v 3 Khawsa a tyihzawih Mosi ingkaw Tuuca a laa ce sa uhy: “Boeimang soeih Bawipa Khawsa, na ik-oeih saikhqi ve kawpoek kyi ak bau soeih na awm hy. Khawhqai qoek sangpahrang, na lamkhqi ve dyng nawh thym hy.  
\v 4 Nang ama nik kqih u nu ak awm kaw, Aw Bawipa nang ming amak zoeksang u nu ak awm kaw? Ikawtih nang doeng ciim hyk ti. Qampum thlang boeih law kawm usaw na haiawh ni bawk kawm uh, kawtih nang a ik-oeih thym saikhqi ce dang hawh hy,” tinawh laa sa uhy.  
\v 5 Cekcoengawh ka hak toek awh khan nakaw bawkim, Awitaaknaak hi im ak awng qu ce hu nyng.  
\v 6 Cawhkaw bawkim khui awhkawng khan ceityih khqih ing tlawhche khqih a law pyi ce hu nyng. Hik ciim ak vang soeih ce bai unawh, amik kqangkhqi ce sui hica ing zen uhy.  
\v 7 Ik-oeih sai ak hqing pupthli khuiawh kaw pynoet ing khan ceityih khqih a venawh kumqui dy ak hqing Khawsa ak kawsonaak ing ak be boet khqih ce pehy.  
\v 8 Cawh bawkim ce Khawsak thaawm boeimangnaak awh zoeksangnaak maikhu ing be hy, khan ceityih khqih a tlawhche khqih ce a boeih hlan dy taw bawkim khuiawh u awm am kun thai hy.   
\c 16  
\p
\v 1 Tempul khuiawh kawng khan ceityih khqih a venawh khawteh na, “Cet nawhtaw, Khawsak kawsonaak boet khqih ce khawmdek awh hawk lah,” tinawh awi ak qeng ce za nyng.   
\p
\v 2 \x - \xo 16:2 \xt Ex. 9.10.\x*A lammanaak khan ceityih ing cet nawh a boet ce khawmdek na nuk hawk hy, cawh ramsatlung ingkaw a myiqawl ak beek thlangkhqi ce ak tlo soeih ingkaw ak che soeih na haai uhy.  
\v 3 A pakkhihnaak khan ceityih ing boet ce tuicun awh hawk bai hy, cawh tui ce thlakthikhqi myihna coeng nawh tui ak khuiawh kaw ramsakhqi boeih boeih ce thi hy.   
\p
\v 4 \x - \xo 16:4 \xt Ex. 7.17-21; Sam 78.44.\x*Apak thumnaak khan ceityihkhqi ing boet ce tuiva ingkaw lawngcakhqi ak khanawh hawk uhy, tui boeih ce thi na coeng hy.  
\v 5 Cawh Tui ak ukkung khan ceityih ing: “Vawhkaw awi dengnaak awh nang ing ak dyng na awideng hyk ti, ak awm huili ingkaw ak awm hawh ak ciim, kawtih nang ing awi ce cemyihna deng hawh hyk ti,  
\v 6 kawtih vekkhqi ing nak thlangciimkhqi ingkaw tawnghakhqi thi a lawng sak a dawngawh, a awk hly tyng thi ce awk sak hawh hyk ti,” tinawh kqawn hy.  
\v 7 Cawh bawkthang benna kawng: “Oeih, boeimang Bawipa Khawsa, nak awidengnaakkhqi ve thym nawh dyng hy,” tinawh hlat pehy.   
\p
\v 8 Khan ceityih a pupthlinaak ing a boet ce khawmik awh hawk nawh khawmik a venawh khawmdek awhkaw thlangkhqi mai ing eng aham awi pehy.  
\v 9 Maihhlawk ing a eng a dawngawh vawhkaw tlawhche ak law sakkung Khawsang ming ce kqawn seet uhy, cehlai zut nawh amah zoeksang aham am ngaih bak bak uhy.   
\p
\v 10 \x - \xo 16:10 \xt Ex. 10.21.\x*Khan ceityih a pumha naak ing boet ce ramsatlung a ngawihdoelh awh hawk hy, cawh a ram ce thannaak khuina tla put hy. Ko ang kqang doena thlangkhqi ing amim lai ai unawh,  
\v 11 haai tlawh dawngawh khan Khawsa ang ming ce kqawn seet uhy. Cehlai ik-oeih sainaak awh am zut bak bak uhy.   
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 16:12 \xt Is. 11.15.\x*Ak kquknaak khan ceityihkhqi ing a boet ce Euphrates tuiva pui awh hawk uhy, cawh tuiva ce kak qup nawh khawlaw benna kaw sangpahrangkhqi ami lawnaak aham lam qoek a bah pehy.  
\v 13 Cekcoengawh uphyih amyihna ak awm qaaiche pakthum ce hu nyng, cekkhqi ce, thlim am khak khuiawh kawng, qamsatlung am kak khui awhkawng, tawngha qawl am khak khui awhkawng thoeng uhy.  
\v 14 Ce mihkhqi cetaw qaai myihlakhqi na awm unawh kawpoek kyi hatnaakkhqi ce sai uhy, khawmdek sangpahrangkhqi boeih a venna cet unawh boeimang Khawsa khawnghi pui awh qaal tuk aham cekkhqi ce pynoet na cawi khqi hy.   
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 16:15 \xt Mat 24.43,44; Luke 12.39,40; Awph 3.3.\x*\wj Ngai lah, quk-ai a myihna law kawng! Ih kaana a hyrpy na awm nawh a pum a zal na chahphyi na ama awm aham hi a oepchoeh na ak ta taw a zoseen hy.”\wj*  
\v 16 \x - \xo 16:16 \xt 2 Kin. 23.29; Zech. 12.11.\x*Hebrai awi na Armageddon ami ti a hunawh cekkhqi ing sangpahrangkhqi ce cun kang uhy.   
\p
\v 17 Khan ceityih ak khqihnaak ing a boet ce khan zilh awh hawk hy, cawh tempul khuiawh kaw ngawihdoelh awhkawng: “Boeih hawh hy,” tinawh awi ce law hy.   
\p
\v 18 \x - \xo 16:18 \xt Awph 8.5; 11.13,19.\x*Cawh khawkphla ingkaw khawnghum awi ing lipi ce khawteh na tat hy. Khawmdek awh thlanghqing a awm plek awhkawng vemih lipi ve tat khawi hlan hy, lipi ce tat hy.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 16:19 \xt Is. 51.17.\x*Khawk bau ce pakthum na pek qu nawh, rampum awhkaw khawk baukhqi ce plawci boeih hy. Khawsa ing Babylon khawk bau ce sim nawh ak kawsonaak misur tui ing ak be boet ce pehy.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 16:20 \xt Awph 6.14.\x*Sanglakkhqi awm cen kang nawh tlangkhqi awm am dang voel hy.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 16:21 \xt Ex. 9.23; Awph 11.19.\x*Khawk khan nakawng pawng zaoet ak rih qeel ce thlangkhqik khanna tla hy. Cawhkaw qeel ce tla nawh kqih a awm a dawngawh Khawsang ming ce kqawnseet uhy.   
\c 17  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 17:1 \xt Jer. 51.13.\x*Boet khqih ak pawm khan ceityih khqih khuiawh kaw pynoet ing ka venawh: “Law lah, tui khawzah awh ak ngawi, pup zawi pyi nu dyna ce nim huh vang.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 17:2 \xt Is. 23.17; Jer. 51.7.\x*Khawmdek sangpahrangkhqi ing anih ing samphaih unawh khawmdek thlangkhqi ce anih a samphaihnaak misur tui ing qui sak boeih hy,” ni tina hy.  
\v 3 Cekcoengawh khan ceityih ing qamkoh na Myihla awh ni ceh pyi hy. Cawh Khawsa thekhanaak ming ing ak be, lu khqih ta nawh kii pahqa ak ta ak thim qamsatlung ak khanawh ak ngawi nu pynoet ce hu nyng.  
\v 4 Ce nu ing ak thim ingkaw ak ling hi ce bai hy, ak vang sui ingkaw lung phuk tlo ingkaw pale ing thoeih ang cam qu hy. A kut awh tyih ak cu ik-oeih ingkaw a samphaihnaak tyih ak cu sui boet ce pawm hy.  
\v 5 A talqi awh vemyihna ca qee awm hy: “PUP ZAWIKRI A NU INGKAW KHAWMDEK AWHKAW TyIH AK CU ANG HyP BAByLON KHAWK BAU.  
\v 6 Cawhkaw nu ce thlakciimkhqi thi, Jesu ak dyihpyi thlangkhqi a thi a qui ce hu hy. Anih ce ka huh awh, kak kawpoek kyi hy.   
\p
\v 7 Cawh khan ceityih ing, kawtih nak kawpoek a kyi? Nu ingkaw ang ngawihnaak a lu khqih ingkaw ak kii pahqa ak ta qamsatlung akoe ang hyp ce nik kqawn pe vang.  
\v 8 Qamsatlung vai na huh ce tuh awhkaw am voel ni, cawhkaw qamsatlung taw a dytnaak amak awm lawk-kqawng khui awhkawng thoeng kawmsaw amah a seetnaak hun na cet kaw. Khawmdek a syn cyk awhkawng hqingnaak cauk awh ang ming amak pa thlangkhqi ing ak awm hawh, cehlai tuh amak awm nawh ak law hly kawi qamsatlung ce ami huh awh amik kawpoek kyi kaw.  
\v 9 Ve ik-oeih awh cyihnaak ngoe hy. Lu khqih cetaw nu ang ngawihnaak tlang khqih ni.  
\v 10 Cekkhqi ce sangpahrang khqih na awm awm bai hy. Pumha tloek taw tlu hawh uhy, tuh pynoet awm hy, ak awm ce law hlan hyn hy; cehlai anih ce a law awh kawlhkalh ni a awm hly.  
\v 11 Ni hu awh ak awm, tuh amak awm ce sangpahrang ak kqeetnaak na awm hy. Anih ce khqih ak khuiawh pa nawh anih awm seetnaak ak khuiawh cet lawt kaw.  
\v 12 Kii pahqa na huh cetaw qam ak hu hlan sangpahrang pahqa tloek ni, cehlai khawnoek pynoet khui sangpahrang saithainaak ce qamsatlung ing dang lawt kawm uh.  
\v 13 Cekkhqi ing cainaak pynoet ni ami taak uh, thaawmnaak ingkaw saithainaak ce qamsatlung a venawh pe kawm uh.  
\v 14 Tuuca ce tu kawm uh, cehlai tuuca ing noeng kaw, kawtih anih taw boeikhqi a Boei ingkaw sangpahrangkhqi a Sangpahrang na a awm a dawngawh – amah ing khy hy, tyk nawh ypawm na a hu awh ak batkhqi ce a venawh awm kawm uh,” ni tina hy.  
\v 15 Cawh khan ceityih ing ka venawh, “Pup zawi nu ang ngawihnaak tui cetaw thlangkhqi, thlang kqeng, phynlum ingkaw awi cawm awi ce khqi ni.  
\v 16 Qamsatlung ingkaw kii pahqa ak law ing cawhkaw pup zawikung ce sawhna kaw. Plawci sak kqawi kawmsaw ak pum a zal na cehta qawi kaw; a sa ce ai kawm nih saw mai awh phum kawm nih.  
\v 17 Ikawtih Khawsa ing cekkhqi kawlung khuiawh amah a ngaihnaak soep sak aham cawhkaw qamsatlung a venawh uk thainaak ce Khawsak awi a soep hlan dy pehy.  
\v 18 Nu na huh cetaw khawmdek sangpahrangkhqi ak ukkung khawk bau ni,” ni tina hy.   
\c 18  
\p
\v 1 Cekcoengawh khawk khan awhkawng anuk kqum law khan ceityih pynoet ce hu nyng. Anih ing saithainaak ak bau soeih ce tahy, a boeimangnaak ing khawmdek coei pheng hy.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 18:2 \xt Is. 21.9; Jer. 51.8; Awph 14.8; \xt Is. 13.21; Jer. 50.39.\x*Awi khawteh na: “Tlu hawh hy! Babylon khawk bau taw tlu hawh hy! Qaaikhqi awmnaak hun na coeng hawh nawh qaihchekhqi thawng tlaknaak hun, amak ciim ingkaw tyih ak kap phakhqi thawng tlaknaak hun na awm hawh hy.   
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 18:3 \xt Is. 23.17; Jer. 51.7.\x*Kawtih thlangphyn khqi ing anih a samphaih qawnaak misur tui awh qui boeih hawh uhy. Khawmdek awhkaw sangpahrangkhqi ing anih samphaih unawh, ik-oeih ak zawikhqi ing anih a awmhlynaak awhkawng boei khqoet khqoet uhy,” tinawh khy hy.   
\p
\v 4 \x - \xo 18:4 \xt Is. 48.20; Jer. 50.8; 51.6,45.\x*Cekcoengawh khan nakawng awi pynoet za bai nyng: “Kak thlangkhqi, anih a thawlhnaak awh am pa unawh anih a thawlh chenaak amna mi zawknaak aham, anih a venawh kawng law lah uh,   
\p
\v 5 \x - \xo 18:5 \xt Gen 18.20,21; Jer. 51.9.\x*kawtih anih a thawlhnaak taw khan dyna hang be nawh, Khawsa ing anih a thawlh sainaak ce sim pehy.   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 18:6 \xt Sam 137.8; Jer. 50.29.\x*Ce nu ing a peek a myihna pe tlaih lawt hy, a ik-oeih sainaak awh ak bawk na pe tlaih hy. Amah a boet awh kqit pe nawh a bawk na pehy.   
\p
\v 7 \x - \xo 18:7 \xt Is. 47.7-9.\x*Amah ingkaw amah ak thlang zoeksangnaak ingkaw a awmhlynaak a myihna khuikhanaak ing ko ang kqangnaak ce pehy. Ak kawk khuiawh taw sangpahrang nu a myihna ak ngawi, hu hai na am awm nyng, ityk awh awm am ko am kqang tikaw, tihy.   
\p
\v 8 Cedawngawh hypoet khuiawh a tlawhche ing anih ce lo kaw: thihnaak, go ang kqangnaak ingkaw khawkhanaak ing anih ce zawl kaw. Mai awh ui kaw, kawtih boeimang Khawsa ing anih ce awi deng hawh hy.   
\p
\v 9 \x - \xo 18:9 \xt Ezek. 26.16,17.\x*Anih ing samphaih haih nawh ak awmhly pyi haih khawmdek sangpahrangkhqi ing mai ak khui ce ami huh awh anih ce kqah kawm usaw lungnat za kawm uh.  
\v 10 A khuikhanaak ce kqih kawm uh, ak hla na dyi hoe kawm usaw kqang kawm uh, khaw map hyk ti! khaw map hyk ti!, Aw khawk bau, Aw Babylon, tha ak awm khawk bau! khawnoek pynoet khuiawh na seetnaak ce pha law hawh hy!   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 18:11 \xt Ezek. 27.31,36.\x*Khawmdek awh ik-oeih ak zawikhqi ingawm anih ce kqah kawm usaw lungnat za kawm uh –  
\v 12 \x - \xo 18:12 \xt Ezek. 27.12,13,22.\x*suikhqi, tangkakhqi, a phu ak tlo lungkhqi ingkaw palekhqi, hi ak leek leekkhqi hawnkeh khqaikhqi, puu a sa ingkaw hik thimkhqi, thing soepkepkhqi, vyi a haa ingkaw a sai ik-oeih soepkep, thingphu ak tlokhqi, qawhumkhqi, thi ingkaw lungbawk,  
\v 13 cinamon ingkaw singhal ak thaihkhqi, bawktui Myrrh ingkaw frankisen, misurtui ingkaw olive situi, vak-kqa cang ingkaw phaihpi vai ak che che khqi vaitaw panaa ingkaw tuikhqi, mirangkhqi ingkaw a ik-oeihkhqi, thlang pum ingkaw ang myihlakhqi ce u ingawm ap thlaih pe voel kaw.   
\p
\v 14 cekkhqi ing, nang ing nang lamtoen ak thaih ce cing hawh hy. Na boeinaakkhqi ingkaw awmhlynaakkhqi ce qeng boeih hawh hy, ityk awh awm am hu voel kawp ti, tina kawm uh.   
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 18:15 \xt Ezek. 27.31,36.\x*Ve ik-oeih zawi nawh ve nu a venna kawng boeinaak ak hu ik-oeih ak zawikhqi ce ak hla na dyi hoe kawm usaw, ce a nu a khuikhanaak ce kqih kawm uh, kqang kawm usaw.   
\p
\v 16 Ko ang kqang doena, “Khaw map hy! Khaw map hy! Aw khawk bau, hik leek leek, hawnkeh khqai ak thim ing thawi ang cam qu tiksaw sui, lung phuk tlo ingkaw pale ingkaw ak vang hlup hlup na, thawi am cam qu hlai hyk ti!   
\p
\v 17 \x - \xo 18:17 \xt Is. 23.14; Ezek. 27.26-30.\x*Khawnoek pynoet khui mai awh cawhkaw byn a baikhqi ce plawci boeih mah hy! Tuicunli awhkaw tui lawng ak uk ingkaw tui lawng awh ak cet thlangkhqi boeih lawng ak kaih thlangkhqi, tuicunli ingkaw phoen ak khut thlangkhqi ce ak hla na dyi hoe kawm uh.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 18:18 \xt Ezek. 27.32.\x*Anih a mai ak khu dung dung ce ami huh awh, vemih khawk bau ve ak awm lawt hy voei nu? ti kawm uh.   
\p
\v 19 \x - \xo 18:19 \xt Ezek. 27.30-34.\x*Dekvai ing a lu awh phul qu kawm usaw, kqung ang kqap doena, “Khaw map hyk ti! khaw map hyk ti, Aw khawk bau, tui awh tui lawng ing ak cet thlangkhqi boeih ing anih a boeinaak ing maw ami boei hlai! Khawnoek pynoet khui mai awh plawci bang mah hy!  
\v 20 \x - \xo 18:20 \xt Deut. 32.43; Jer. 51.48.\x*Aw khan nang, anih ak khanawh zeel lah! thlakciimkhqi ingkaw ceityihkhqi ingkaw tawnghakhqi zeel lah uh! Anih ing nangmih ani thekhanaak a myihna Khawsa ing ak khanawh awi deng hawh hy,” ti uhy.   
\p
\v 21 \x - \xo 18:21 \xt Jer. 51.63,64; \xt Ezek. 26.21.\x*Cekcoengawh khan ceityih pynoet ing cang netnaak teh ak law lung ak bau soeih ce lo nawh tuicunli khuina ak khawng coengawh, “Vemih khuikhanaak ing Babylon khawk bau taw khawng na awm kaw, ityk awm huh voel na am awm voel kaw.   
\p
\v 22 \x - \xo 18:22 \xt Ezek. 26.13; Is. 24.8.\x*\x - \xo 18:22 \xt Jer. 7.34; 25.10.\x*Tingtoeng ingkaw tumding ak tumkhqi, phung ak tumkhqi, uut ak yngkhqi ce ityk awh awm nang ak khui awhkawng zaaknaak am awm voel kaw.   
\p
\v 23 Mai-im awhkaw maivang awm u ing am hu voel kaw. Zu ak lo ingkaw va ak ta hly kawi cadawng nulaa ak awi awm u ing nang ak khuiawh am za voel kaw. Nang ak khuiawh ik-oeih ak zawikhqi ce khawmdek awhkawng thlak bau na awm uhy. Nang a kutlam thoemnaak ingkaw qam boeih boeih ce lam hang sak hawh hyk ti.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 18:24 \xt Jer. 51.49.\x*Anih ak khuiawh tawnghakhqi ingkaw thlakciimkhqi thi ingkaw khawmdek awh ami him thlangkhqi a thi ce awm hy,” tinawh kqawn hy.   
\c 19  
\p
\v 1 Vemyihkhqi a awm coengawh khan na thlang kqeng khawzah ak awi ce za nyng: “Halleluiah! Hulnaak, thangleeknaak ingkaw thaawmnaak taw ningnih Khawsa a koe ni,  
\v 2 kawtih a awidengnaak taw dyng nawh thym hy. A samphaihnaak ingkaw khawmdek ak plawci sakkung, pup zawi nu ce dawk palh sak hawh hy. A tyihzawihkhqi a thi phu ce anih a venawh lo hawh hy,” tinawh khy uhy.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 19:3 \xt Is. 34.10.\x*Cekcoengawh khy tlaih bai uhy, “Halleluiah! Anih a maikhu taw kumqui dyna nang khu hawh hy,” ti uhy.   
\p
\v 4 A hqamca a thong pupthli ingkaw ik-oeih sai hqing pupthli ing tluuk doena ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi Khawsa ce bawk uhy. “Amen, Halleluiah,” ti uhy.  
\v 5 Cekcoengawh ngawihdoelh awhkawng, “Amah ak kqih, a tyihzawih, thlak zawi thlak bau boeih, ningnih a Khawsa ce kyih lah uh,” tinawh khy uhy.  
\v 6 Cekcoengawh thlang kqeng khawzah thlang ak awi amyihna, tuibau awi ingkaw khawnghum awi amyihna, “Halelluiah! Ikawtih ningnih a Bawipa Boeimang Khawsa ing uk hy.  
\v 7 Cedawngawh zeel u seitaw amah ce thangleek sak lah u sih! Ikawtih tuuca a zulawhnaak taw law hawh hy, a lawh hly kawi nula awm coekqoek na awm hawh hy.  
\v 8 Hik leek, ak ciim ingkaw ak vang ce thoeih ang cam qunaak na pe hawh hy, tinawh khy uhy. (Hik leek taw thlakciimkhqi a ik-oeih sai huh saknaak na awm hy.)  
\v 9 \x - \xo 19:9 \xt Mat 22.2,3.\x*Cekcoengawh khan ceityih ing ka venawh, “Ree lah: Tuuca zulawhnaak awh ak khy thlangkhqi taw ami zoseen hy!” ni tina hy. Cekcoengawh, “Ve ve Khawsak awi tang tang ni,” ni tina bai hy.   
\p
\v 10 Cedawngawh anih ce bawk aham a khawkung awh tlunyng. Cehlai ka venawh, “Cemyihna koeh sai! Kai taw nang ingkaw Jesu ak dyihpyi na koeinaakhqi amyihna tyihzawih nani ka awm lawt. Khawsa bawk lah! Ikawtih Jesu ak awihkqawn taw myihla awiphawngnaak ni,” ni tina hy.  
\v 11 Khan ak awng qu ingkaw ka haiawh meqang bawk ak dyi ce hu nyng, cawh ak ngawi taw ypawm ingkaw Thym mingna hy. Ak thym na awi deng nawh qaal thawh hy.  
\v 12 A mik kqawi taw mai amyihna vang nawh, a lu awhkaw boei lumyk khawzah awm hy. U ingawm ama sim amah doeng ing a sim ming ce a pum awh qee na awm kaw.  
\v 13 Thi awh ak chum hi ce bai hy, ang ming taw Khawsak awi mingna hy.  
\v 14 Mirang bawk awh ak ngawi ak khan qalkapkhqi ing hik bawk leek soeih ce bai unawh a hu awh bat u hy.  
\v 15 Anih am khak khui awhkawng qamkhqi tlyhnaak aham zawzi ak hqat soeih ce thoeng hy. “Anih ing thi sawnghqawl ing cekkhqi ce uk kaw.” Boeimang Khawsa ak kawsonaak misurtui suinaak anih ing leh hy.  
\v 16 A hi ingkaw a phai awh ve ang ming ve awm hy: \sc Boikri A Boi Ing Sangpahrang Kri A Sangpahrang\sc*.   
\p
\v 17 \x - \xo 19:17 \xt Ezek. 39.17-20.\x*Khawmik awh ak dyi khan ceityih pynoet ce hu nyng, anih ing khan na ak ding phakhqi boeih a venawh, “Law lah uh, Khawsa a buh veel aham cun lah uh,  
\v 18 sangpahrangkhqi, qalboeikhqi, thlak baukhqi, meqangkhqi ingkaw ak khanawh ak ngawikhqi, thlakzawi, thlakbau thlang thawt ingkaw tamnaakhqi a sa ce ai lah uh,” tina hy.  
\v 19 Cekcoengawh qamsatlung ingkaw khawmdek awhkaw sangpahrangkhqi ing meqang awh ak ngawi ingkaw a qalkapkhqi ce tuk aham qalkapkhqi ce cawi uhy.  
\v 20 Cehlai qamsatlung ingkaw anih ang zyng na kawpoek kyi hatnaak ak sai tawngha qawl ce tuk uhy. Kawpoek kyi hatnaak sainaak ak caming qamsatlung hatnaak ak takhqi ingkaw myiqawl ak bawkkhqi ce anih ing thai na hy. Cekkqawi ce kat mai tuili khuina a hqing na nuk khawng uhy.  
\v 21 Ak changkhqi cetaw meqang awh ak ngawi kha khui awhkawng ak thoeng law zawzi ing him boeih hy, khan phakhqi ing a mingmih a sa ce ak phyi kynkqyng na ai uhy.   
\c 20  
\p
\v 1 A dytnaak amak awm lawk-kqawng cabi ingkaw kenqui pawm law nawh khan nakawng anuk law khan ceityih pynoet ce hu nyng.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 20:2 \xt Gen 3.1.\x*Anih ing thlim, syn awhkaw khqui kqym Setan ce tuk nawh kum thongoet khui thawng thla hy.  
\v 3 a dytnaak amak awm lawk-kqawng khuina khawng hy, kum thongoet a boeih hlan dy qampum awhkawng thlang ama thainaak thai ham chawh a khaih coengawh cabi khaih sih hy. Cekcoengawh kawlkalh khuiawh loet sak kaw.  
\v 4 Awideng thainaak ak hu thlangkhqi ngawihdoelh awh amik ngawi ce hu nyng. Jesu ak awi ingkaw Khawsak awi a ming dyihpyi a dawngawh a hawng awh amik tlyh ang myihla ce hu nyng. Vekkhqi ing qamsatlung ingkaw a myi ce am bawk unawh a talqi ingkaw a kut awh hatnaak awm am ta uhy. A mingmih ce hqing unawh Khrih ingqawi kum thong oet khui boei na uk uhy.  
\v 5 (Kum thongoet a boeih hlan dy ak changkhqi taw am hqing uhy.) Ve ve lamma cyk thawhnaak na awm hy.  
\v 6 Lamma cyk thawhnaak awh ak pakhqi taw zo ak seenkhqi ingkaw ak ciimkhqi na awm uhy. Thihnaak apakkhih ing cekkhqik khanawh ikaw saithainaak am ta voel kaw, cekkhqi taw Khawsa ing Khrih a khawsoeih na awm kawm usaw Khrih ing kum thongoet khui uk haih kawm uh.   
\p
\v 7 Kum thongoet a boeih coeng awhtaw setan ce thawngim khui awhkawng hlah tlaih kaw,  
\v 8 Khawmdek kil phli awh ak awm qampum thlang ce thainaak aham cet kaw – cetaw Gog ingkaw Magog ni – qaal tuk aham thlang cawi kaw. A doem naak benna taw tuicun ceng awhkaw dizui zah law uhy.  
\v 9 Khawmdek a boet voel dyna tho unawh Khawsa ing a lungnaak, Khawsa a awmnaak khawk bau ce chung uhy, cehlai khawk khan nakawng mai nung tla law nawh cekkhqi ce ui boeih uhy.  
\v 10 Cekcoengawh a mingmih ak thainaakkung qaai ce qamsatlung ingkaw tawngha qawlkhqi ak khawngnaak kat mai tuili khuina khawng hy. Than dai kumqui dy ce a hun awh khuikha kawm uh.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 20:11 \xt Dan. 7.9,10.\x*Ngawihdoelh bawk ingkaw ak cheiawh ak ngawi thlang ce hu nyng, khawmdek ingkaw khan ce a hai awhkawng dawng unawh a awmnaak hun am ta voel uhy.  
\v 12 Cawh thlakthi ak zawi ak bau ngawihdoelh a haiawh dyi unawh cauk ak awng qu hyt ce hu nyng. Ak chang cauk pynoet ak awng qu ce awm hu nyng. Cawhkaw cauk cetaw hqingnaak cauk ni, cauk awh qee amyihna thlakthikhqi ce awideng hy.  
\v 13 Tuicun awhkaw ak thikhqi ce tuicun ing pe law nawh, thihnaak ingkaw Hades ing lo hy, thlakthikhqi awm pe tlaih hy, thlang boeih ce a mimah a ik-oeih sai amyihna awideng boeih hy.  
\v 14 Thihnaak ingkaw Hades te mai tuili na khawng hy. Cawhkaw mai tuili cetaw a voeihih thihnaak ni.  
\v 15 Hqingnaak cauk awh ming amak pa thlang cetaw mai tuili na khawng uhy.   
\c 21  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 21:1 \xt Is. 65.17; 66.22; 2Pe 3.13.\x*Cekcoengawh khan thai ingkaw dek thai ce hu nyng, lamma awhkaw khan ingkaw dek cetaw khum hawh hy, tuicun awm am awm voel hy.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 21:2 \xt Is. 52.1; \xt Awph 3.12; \xt Is. 61.10.\x*Va ak ta hly kawi nula ing a va aham a thawicam qu hqeet a myihna, Khawsa a venawh kawng Khawk bau Ciim, Jerusalem thai anuk law ce hu nyng.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 21:3 \xt Ezek. 37.27; Lev. 26.11,12.\x*Bawkthang awhkawng awi khawteh na, “Tuh taw Khawsa a awmnaak ce thlanghqing a venawh awm hawh hy, cekkhqi mi awm haih hawh kaw. Cekkhqi ce amah ak thlang na awm kawm uh, Khawsa amah ce cekkhqi mi awm haih kawmsaw a mingmih a Khawsa na awm kaw.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 21:4 \xt Is. 25.8; \xt Is. 35.10; 65.19.\x*Ami mikphli tui boeih boeih ce huih pe hawh kaw. Thihnaak, lungnat zaaknaak, ko ang kqangnaak ingkaw kqangnaak am awm voel kaw, kawtih ik-oeih kqymkhqi cetaw khum bat hawh hy,” tinawh ak khy awi ce za nyng.  
\v 5 Ngawihdoelh awh ak ngawi ing, “Ik-oeih boeih boeih ak thai na sai pan hawh nyng!” tihy. Cekcoengawh, “Ve ve qee lah, kawtih vawhkaw awikhqi vetaw ypnaak awm nawh thym hy,” ni tina hy.   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 21:6 \xt Is. 55.1.\x*Ka venawh, Coeng boeih hawh hy. Kai taw Alpha ingkaw Omega, Grannaak ingkaw Boetnaak na awm nyng. Tui ak ngaih taw hqingnaak tui ak lawng ce a phu peek kaana awk sak kawng.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 21:7 \xt 2 Sam. 7.14; Sam 89.26,27.\x*Noengnaak ak ta thlang ing vemyihkhqi boeih ve pang kaw, anih a Khawsa na awm kawng nyngsaw anih ce ka ca na awm kaw.  
\v 8 Cehlai kqina ak ngetkhqi, amak cangnaak thlangkhqi, boeksekhqi, thlang ak himkhqi, amak thym na nu pa thawlhnaak ak saikhqi, kutlam ak toek thlangkhqi, myi ak beekkhqi ingkaw qaai ak kqawnkhqi – vemih thlangkhqi hamna a kat mai tuili ce awm hy. Ve ve a voeihih thihnaak na awm hy,” ni tina hy.   
\p
\v 9 Nat khqih ing ak be boet khqih ak ta khan ceityih khqih ak khuiawh kaw khan ceityih pynoet ing ka venawh, “Law lah, Tuuca a zu, va ak ta hly nula ce nim huh vang,” ni tina hy.   
\p
\v 10 \x - \xo 21:10 \xt Ezek. 40.2.\x*Anih ing Myihla ak caming tlang ak bau soeih ingkaw ak sang soeih na ni ceh pyi nawh, Khawsa a venna kawng anuk law Jerusalem, Khawk bau Ciim ce nim huh hy.  
\v 11 Cawhkaw awipui cetaw Khawsa boeimangnaak ing vang theng hy, a vangnaak taw lung phu ak tlo soeih jasper lung amyihna vang nawh crystal amyihna caih hy.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 21:12 \xt Ezek. 48.30-35.\x*Ce khawk bau ak chungnaak vawngsang soeih ingkaw ak bau soeih awm nawh, chawh pahqa hlaihih awm hy, chawh boeih awh khan ceityih pahqa hlaihih awm bai hy. Chawh boeih awh Isarael pilnam pahqa hlaihih ming ce qee hy.  
\v 13 Khaw law benawh chawh pakthum, thlung benna chawh pakthum, kham benna chawh pakthum ingkaw khawtlaak benna chawh pakthum awm hy.  
\v 14 Khawk bau ak chungnaak vawng ce tung pahqa hlaihih awm hy, cawhkaw tung awh ceityih pahqa hlaihih ang ming ce awm hy.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 21:15 \xt Ezek. 40.3.\x*Kai ing awi ak kqawn khan ceityih ing khawk bau, vawng ingkaw chawh tahnaak aham sui tahnaak ce pawm hy.  
\v 16 Khawk bau cetaw a kil pupthli law hy, sang awm sang nawh kau awm kau hy. A tahnaak ing khawk bau ce a tah awh a sang stedia 12,000 law nawh a kau ingkaw a sang awm myih qu boeih hy.  
\v 17 Khawk bau awhkaw vawng ce a tah bai awh thlanghqing tahnaak awhtaw dawng 144 sang nawh sah hy, ce ce khan ceityih ing hawna hy.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 21:18 \xt Is. 54.11,12.\x*Cawhkaw vawng cetaw jasper lung ing sai nawh, khawk bau cetaw sui hqoeng na a awm coengawh hlalang a myihna caih hy.   
\p
\v 19 Khawk bau ak chungnaak vawng a tungling cetaw lung phuk tlo soepkep ing thoeihcam hy. A lamma cyknaak ce jasper, a pak khihnaak ce sapphire, apak thumnaak ce chalcedony, a pupthlinaak ce emeraled,  
\v 20 a pumhanaak ce sardonyx, ak kquknaak ce carnelian, ak khqihnaak ce chrysolite, ak kqeetnaak ce beryl, ak kownaak ce topaz, a pahqa naak ce chrysoprase, a hlaioetnaak ce jacinth na awm nawh a hlaihihnaak ce amethyst na awm hy.   
\p
\v 21 Chawh pahqa hlaihih tloek ce pale na awm nawh chawh pynoet qip ce pale ing sai hy. Khawk bau ak khuiawh kaw lam cetaw sui lam na awm nawh, hlalang a myihna caih hy.   
\p
\v 22 Khawk bau ak khuiawh bawkim am awm hy, Boeimang Bawipa Khawsa ingkaw Tuuca ce bawkim na awm hawh hy.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 21:23 \xt Is. 60.19,20.\x*Ce khawk bau ing khawkdai ingkaw pihla vang awm am ngoe voel hy, Khawsa boeimangnaak ing vang sak nawh, Tuuca ce maivang na awm hy.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 21:24 \xt Is. 60.3.\x*Rampum thlangkhqi ing cawhkaw vangnaak awh cet kawm usaw, khawmdek sangpahrangkhqi ing a boeimangnaak ce kun pyi kawm uh.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 21:25 \xt Is. 60.11.\x*Ityk awh awm chawh ce am khai qu kawmsaw, khawmthan awm am awm voel kaw.  
\v 26 Qampum awhkaw boeimang naak ing zoeksangnaak ce ak khuina kun pyi kawm uh.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 21:27 \xt Is. 52.1; Ezek. 44.9.\x*Ikaw awm amak ciim cetaw ce ak khuina am kun qoe qoe kaw, chahqai ik-oeih ak saikhqi ingkaw thlak thaikhqi am kun kawm usaw, Tuuca hqingnaak cabu khuiawh ming qee na ak awmkhqi doeng kun kawm uh.   
\c 22  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 22:1 \xt Ezek. 47.1; Zech. 14.8.\x*Cek coengwh khan ceityih ing hqingnaak tuiva, crystal a myihna ak caih, Khawsa ngawihdoelh ingkaw Tuuca ngawihdoelh awhkawng  
\v 2 \x - \xo 22:2 \xt Gen 2.9.\x*khawk bau a lam lakli awh a nuk lawng law ce nim huh hy. Cawhkaw hqingnaak tuiva cengawh hqingnaak thing ce dyi hy, hla qoek awh voei hra hlaihih qah poepa hy. Cawhkaw thinghah cetaw thlangphyn khqi qoeinaak na awm hy.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 22:3 \xt Zech. 14.11; Gen 3.17.\x*Cawhtaw awihkha phawhnaak ingkaw khawsi zawknaak am awm voel kaw. Khawsa ingkaw Tuuca a ngawihdoelh ce khawk bau khuiawh awm kawmsaw, a tyihzoeihkhqi ing bibi pe kawm uh.  
\v 4 Anih a haai ce hu kawm usaw, ami talqikhqi awh anih ang ming ce awm kaw.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 22:5 \xt Is. 60.19; \xt Dan. 7.18.\x*Khawmthan am awm voel kaw, Mai vang am ngoe voel kawm usaw khawkdai awm am ngoe voel kawm uh, kawtih Bawipa Khawsa ing vangnaak ce pek khqi kaw. A mingmih ing kumqui dy uk hawh kawm uh.  
\v 6 Khan ceityih ing ka venawh, “Vawhkaw awikhqi vetaw thym nawh a ypawm hy. Bawipa, tawnghakhqi myihla Khawsa ing ak awm hly kawi ik-oeih ce a tyihzoeihkhqi venawh huh aham ak khan ceityih ce tyi hy,” ni tina hy.   
\p
\v 7 \wj Ngai lah uh, law nai hawh kawng! Ve cabu ak khui awhkaw awiphawng ak khoem thlang taw a zoseen hy.”\wj*   
\p
\v 8 Kai, Johan ing vawhkaw ik-oeihkhqi ve za nyng saw hu nyng. Vawhkaw ik-oeihkhqi ve za nyng saw ka huh awh, ve ik-oeihkhqi anik huhkung khan ceityih ce bawk aham a khawkung awh tlunyng.  
\v 9 Cehlai anih ing ka venawh, “Cemyihna koeh sai! Kai taw nangmih ingkaw nami koeinaa tawnghakhqi ing ve cauk ak khuiawh kaw awi ak khoemkhqi amyihna tyihzawih nani ka awm lawt. Khawsa bawk lah,” ni tina hy.  
\v 10 Cekcoengawh anih ing, “Ve cauk awhkaw awiphawngkhqi ve koeh khai, kawtih a tym taw zoe hawh hy.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 22:11 \xt Dan. 12.10.\x*Ik-oeih thawlh ak saikhqi taw sai mai seitaw boekse thlangkhqi cetaw ami boe se mai cang seh; ik-oeih thym ak saikhqi ingawm ak thym ik-oeih ce sai poe u seitaw; ak ciim thlang cetaw ciim poe seh,” ni tina hy.   
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 22:12 \xt Is. 40.10; 62.11; \xt Sam 28.4; Is. 40.10; Jer. 17.10.\x*\wj Ngai lah law nai hawh kawng! Kutdo laksawng ik-oeih haw law kawng nyngsaw, thlang ing bi a binaak a myihna pe kawng. \wj* 
\v 13 \x - \xo 22:13 \xt Awph 1.8; \xt Is. 44.6; 48.12; Awph 1.17; 2.8.\x*\wj Kai taw Alpha ingkaw Omega, lamma cyk ingkaw hudyt khyt, akung ingkaw a dawng na awm nyng. \wj* 
\v 14 \x - \xo 22:14 \xt Gen 2.9; 3.22.\x*\wj Hi caih na ak chuk thlangkhqi ing hqingnaak thikthaih ce ai thai kawm usaw khawk bau chawh khuiawh kun thai kawm uh. \wj* 
\v 15 \wj A ceng nakawng thlangkhqi cetaw uikhqi, miklet ak saikhqi, nu pa amak thym na amik pawl qukhqi, thlang ak himkhqi, myi ak bawkkhqi ingkaw ik-oeih amak thym sai ak lungnaak thlangkhqi na awm uhy. \wj* 
\v 16 \x - \xo 22:16 \xt Is. 11.1,10.\x*\wj Kai Jesu ing vawhkaw awi ve thlangboelkhqi ham nangmih a venawh peek aham kak khan ceityih tyi law hawh nyng. Kai taw David ak Gra ingkaw cadil na awm nyngsaw Myncang Thaike na awm nyng,”\wj* ni tina hy.   
\p
\v 17 \x - \xo 22:17 \xt Is. 55.1.\x*Myihla ingkaw va ak ta hly kawi nula ing, “Law lah!” ni tina hy. “Law lah!” tinaak awi ak zaak ak thlang taw law seh. U awm tui ak ngaih taw, law seh; U awm ak ngaih ingtaw, hqingnaak tui ce a zoe na lo lah seh.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 22:18 \xt Deut. 4.2; 12.32.\x*Ve cabu ak awiphawng amik za uh a venawh awm qalqingnaak awi pe nyng, U ingawm vawhkaw awipeek ve a tawm awhtaw, Khawsa ing ve cabu awh ak kqawn tlawhche ce anih aham tawm pe lawt kaw.  
\v 19 U ingawm ve cabu awhkaw awiphawng ve a zuuk thoem awhtaw, ve cabu awh ak kqawn anih ing a huh hly kawi khawciim khui awhkaw hqingnaak thing ce zuuk pe lawt kaw.   
\p
\v 20 Vawhkaw ik-oeihkhqi ak dyihpyikung ing, \wj “Oeih, law nai hawh kawng,”\wj* tihy. Amen. Bawipa Jesu law hlah.  
\v 21 Bawipa Jesu Khrih am qeennaak Khawsak thlangkhqi venawh awm seh. Amen.   